and%20emerging%20obstacles%2C%20such%20as%20the%20gender%20gap%20in%20funding%20or%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chronicle.com%2Farticle%2Fhere-are-the-states-where-lawmakers-are-seeking-to-ban-colleges-dei-efforts%3Fsra%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewave%20of%20anti-DEI%20bills%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20laws%20sweeping%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20celebration%20drew%20top%20dogs%20who%20dispensed%20their%20entrepreneurial%20advice%2C%20as%20well%20as%20up-and-comers%20who%20pitched%20their%20business%20ideas.%20Here%20are%20some%20of%20the%20big%20names%20who%20attended.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESue%20Wagner%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221086%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sue%20Wagner%20smiles%20with%20Wendy%20Diamond.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6568eeaa58e7c0c29a2875f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22724%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESue%20Wagner%20with%20Wendy%20Diamond.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20WEDO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESue%20Wagner%2C%20a%20cofounder%20and%20former%20vice%20chairman%20of%20the%20investment%20firm%20BlackRock%2C%20discussed%20part%20of%20her%20origin%20story%20during%20the%20summit.%20She%20said%20that%20two%20of%20the%20firm's%20eight%20original%20founders%20in%201988%20were%20women%2C%20which%20was%20%26quot%3Bunheard%20of%20then%26quot%3B%20and%20is%20still%20rare%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20room%2C%20we%20are%20reminded%20how%20important%20it%20is%20to%20have%20role%20models%20and%20to%20be%20role%20models%2C%20to%20show%20up%20and%20be%20visible%2C%20and%20insist%20on%20equal%20and%20equitable%20opportunities%2C%26quot%3B%20Wagner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWomen's%20rights%20and%20affirmative%20action%20are%20under%20assault%20here%20and%20around%20the%20world.%20DEI%20shaming%20has%20taken%20root%2C%20threatening%20hard-won%20progress.%20Oppression%20persists%2C%20and%20violent%20heinous%20crimes%20ag