2content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221320%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alex%20Grendi%20is%20a%20men's%20sex%20coach.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656796a8c58b6f84123b79e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22990%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlex%20Grendi%20is%20a%20men's%20sex%20coach.%20He's%20helped%20more%20than%20250%20men%20learn%20to%20have%20satisfying%20partnered%20sex%20through%20his%20virtual%20%243%2C000%20course.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Alex%20Grendi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMens'%20sex%20coach%20Alex%20Grendi%20says%20changing%20his%20mindset%20around%20intimacy%20transformed%20his%20sex%20life%20for%20the%20better.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGrendi%20said%20four%20tips%20helped%20him%20make%20partnered%20sex%20more%20pleasurable%20for%20him%20and%20his%20partners.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFollowing%20these%20tips%20can%20turn%20even%20one-night%20stands%20into%20amazing%20sex%2C%20Grendi%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20week%2C%20Alex%20Grendi%20gets%20on%20Zoom%20with%20eight%20men%2C%20fielding%20their%20questions%20about%20how%20to%20impress%20their%20female%20partners%20in%20bed%20and%20ways%20to%20maximize%20their%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsex-coach-career-premature-ejaculation-erectile-dysfunction-course-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emen's%20sex%20coach%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Grendi%20has%20helped%20hundreds%20of%20men%20have%20the%20best%20sex%20of%20their%20lives%2C%20the%20kind%20that%20makes%20their%20female%20partners%20gush%20to%20their%20friends%20about%20how%20mind-blowing%20it%20was%20for%20them%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrendi%20does%20this%20through%20his%2012-week%20virtual%20course%2C%20which%20includes%2072%20sex%20lessons%20and%20weekly%20group%20check-ins.%20For%20%243%2C000%2C%20Grendi's%20clients%20get%20lifetime%20access%20to%20his%20video%20modules%2C%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20lessons%2C%20which%20focus%20on%20things%20like%20personal%20arousal%20and%20female%20pleasure%2C%20are%20useful%20for%20both%20single%20and%20partnered%20men%2C%20according%20to%20Grendi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20he's%20tried%20all%20of%20his%20tips%2C%20both%20while%20in%20relationships%20and%20single%2C%20finding%20that%20even%20casual%20hookups%20could%20be%20deeply%20satisfying%20when%20he%20took%20the%20right%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20using%20these%20tips%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20perform%20like%20a%20porn%20star%20without%20really%20considering%20my%20or%20my%20partner's%20desires.%20Now%2C%20I'm%20having%20the%20best%20sex%20of%20my%20life.%20I%20feel%20complete%20confidence%20and%20control%2C%20can%20last%20as%20long%20as%20I%20want%2C%20and%20help%20my%20partners%20have%20some%20of%20the%20deepest%20and%20most%20expansive%20orgasms%20of%20their%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20Grendi%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%2C%20Grendi%20shares%20his%20four%20top%20takeaways%20for%20men%20who%20want%20to%20have%20better%20sex.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EReduce%20stress%20in%20your%20day-to-day%20life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Grendi's%20sex%20coaches%20helped%20him%20realize%20that%20taking%20care%20of%20your%20mental%20health%20is%20important%20for%20a%20satisfying%20sex%20life%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20then%2C%20Grendi%20said%20he%20didn't%20take%20much%20time%20for%20himself%20to%20calm%20down%20after%20a%20stressful%20day%20at%20work%2C%20let%20alone%20before%20a%20date%20that%20could%20result%20in%20sex.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20he%20started%20taking%20time%20to%20reduce%20daily%20stress%20%E2%80%94%20exercising%2C%20and%20swapping%20morning%20doom-scrolling%20on%20his%20phone%20for%20reading%20a%20book%20or%20going%20for%20a%20walk%20%E2%80%94%20Grendi%20noticed%20that%20he%20could%20enter%20sexual%20experiences%20with%20a%20more%20grounded%20and%20less%20anxious%20demeanor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20just%20be%20going%20100%20miles%20an%20hour%20all%20day%20and%20then%20expect%20you%20can%20just%20switch%20that%20off%20at%209%20PM%20and%20be%20totally%20calm%20and%20ready%20for%20pleasure.%20You%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20regulate%20your%20nervous%20system%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Grendi%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20assume%20every%20partner%20wants%20the%20same%20things%20during%20sex%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGrendi%20also%20learned%20how%20to%20focus%20on%20his%20sexual%20partners%20in%20more%20helpful%20ways%2C%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20working%20with%20sex%20coaches%2C%20he%20fixated%20on%20how%20a%20partner%20might%20judge%20his%20performance%20after%20sex%2C%20or%20what%20she%20might%20tell%20her%20friends.%20But%20Grendi's%20female%20sex%20coach%20taught%20him%20that%20turning%20his%20attention%20to%20how%20each%20individual%20partner%20likes%20to%20receive%20pleasure%20was%20a%20better%20strategy%20for%20improving%20his%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrendi%20said%20that%20she%20taught%20him%20about%20the%20concept%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sexloveandot.com%2Fpost%2Fpleasure-mapping%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epleasure%20mapping%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20slowly%20touching%20different%20areas%20of%20a%20partner's%20body%20and%20genitals%20to%20understand%20what%20they%20personally%20want%20and%20need%20to%20get%20off%2C%20and%20which%20areas%20to%20avoid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20started%20to%20do%20this%20with%20new%20partners%2C%20they%20would%20tell%20me%20that%20they've%20never%20been%20touched%20like%20this%20before.%20It's%20been%20pretty%20special%20to%20help%20partners%20connect%20to%20their%20pleasure%20or%20have%20orgasms%20in%20new%20ways%2C%26quot%3B%20Grendi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20pleasure%20mapping%20doesn't%20center%20penetrative%20sex%2C%20it%20became%20a%20way%20for%20Grendi%20to%20focus%20less%20on%20his%20penis%20and%20more%20on%20pleasure%20as%20a%20full-body%20experience%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EExperiment%20with%20touch%20when%20you're%20alone%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20men's%20sex%20coach%20taught%20Grendi%20the%20importance%20of%20self-touch%20for%20becoming%20a%20better%20sexual%20partner%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20he%20did%20with%20his%20partners%2C%20Grendi%20committed%20to%20touching%20himself%20all%20over%2C%20not%20just%20his%20genitals.%20He%20said%20he%20still%20sets%20aside%20an%20hour%20each%20week%20%E2%80%94%20usually%20three%2020-minute%20sessions%20%E2%80%94%20to%20be%20alone%20and%20experiment%20with%20feel-good%20sensations%2C%20like%20lightly%20biting%20his%20arm%20or%20scratching%20his%20chest.%20This%20practice%20has%20never%20gotten%20in%20the%20way%20of%20his%20sexual%20relationships%2C%20Grendi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Grendi%2C%20this%20practice%20made%20him%20realize%20there%20were%20so%20many%20more%20ways%20to%20feel%20pleasure%20than%20he%20knew%20was%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExploring%20every%20part%20of%20your%20body%20is%20a%20huge%20factor%20in%20knowing%20what%20you%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20Grendi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPractice%20being%20comfortable%20with%20saying%20%26quot%3Bno%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Grendi%20explored%20his%20body%2C%20he%20also%20learned%20the%20types%20of%20sensations%20he%20doesn't%20like%20during%20partnered%20intimacy%2C%20like%20being%20touched%20on%20the%20lips%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20someone's%20doing%20that%20and%20I%20don't%20say%20anything%2C%20I'm%20just%20going%20to%20be%20thinking%2C%20'Wow%2C%20this%20is%20the%20last%20thing%20I%20want%20right%20now%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20ruin%20the%20mood%2C'%26quot%3B%20Grendi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20one%20of%20his%20male%20sex%20coaches%20taught%20him%20how%20to%20avoid%20this%20outcome%2C%20instilling%20in%20him%20the%20importance%20of%20saying%20%26quot%3Bno%26quot%3B%20to%20someone%20in%20a%20sexual%20setting%20without%20feeling%20guilty%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20I'll%20be%20like%2C%20'Hey%2C%20please%20be%20mindful%20not%20to%20touch%20my%20face.%20I%20like%20it%20more%20if%20you%20touch%20my%20neck%2C'%26quot%3B%20Grendi%20said.%20He%20told%20Insider%20that%20this%20practice%20has%20been%20a%20%26quot%3Bgame-changer%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20sex%20life%20because%20it%20makes%20sex%20feel%20more%20like%20a%20collaboration%20between%20partners%2C%20rather%20than%20a%20self-sacrificing%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-be-better-at-sex-men-coach-tips-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701525061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656799e5fd6200867dd0b851%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-be-better-at-sex-men-coach-tips-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22To%20be%20a%20better%20lover%2C%20men's%20sex%20coach%20Alex%20Grendi%20recommends%20pleasure%20mapping%20each%20partner%20to%20learn%20what%20they%20like%20and%20experimenting%20with%20self-touch.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jnaftulin%40insider.com%20(Julia%20Naftulin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-be-better-at-sex-men-coach-tips-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Vampire'%20stars%20could%20be%20using%20galactic%20henchmen%20to%20help%20feed%20on%20their%20companions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20blue%20star%20with%20a%20smaller%20blue%20star%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656663b0fd6200867dd06256%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221563%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EArtist's%20impression%20composed%20of%20a%20star%20with%20a%20disc%20around%20it%20(a%20type-Be%20%26quot%3Bvampire%26quot%3B%20star%3B%20foreground)%20and%20its%20companion%20star%20that%20has%20been%20stripped%20of%20its%20outer%20parts%20(background).%3Cp%3EESO%2FL.%20Cal%C3%A7ada%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EType-Be%20stars%2C%20nicknamed%20%26quot%3Bvampire%26quot%3B%20stars%2C%20are%20believed%20to%20strip%20the%20mass%20of%20a%20nearby%20star.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EScientists%20are%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20this%20happens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENew%20research%20shows%20that%20a%20third%20star%20might%20be%20facilitating%20the%20mass%20transfer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMassive%20%26quot%3Bvampire%26quot%3B%20stars%20that%20feast%20on%20their%20celestial%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecompanions%20could%20be%20assisted%20by%20a%20third%2C%20hidden%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjames-webb-telescope-new-image-milky-way-colorful-heart-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20new%20research%20in%20the%20peer-reviewed%20journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fmnras%2Farticle%2F527%2F2%2F3076%2F7310873%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMonthly%20Notices%20of%20the%20Royal%20Astronomical%20Society%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EType-Be%20stars%2C%20characterized%20by%20their%20large%20size%20and%20surrounding%20rings%20of%20gas%2C%20are%20a%20subset%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.britannica.com%2Fscience%2FB-type-star%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etype-B%20stars%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20very%20hot%2C%20bright%2C%20and%20blue.%20The%20subtype%20makes%20up%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aanda.org%2Farticles%2Faa%2Fabs%2F2020%2F09%2Faa37640-20%2Faa37640-20.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E20%25%20of%20the%20type-B%20star%20population%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Jonathan%20Dodd%2C%20a%20Ph.D.%20student%20and%20one%20of%20the%20study's%20lead%20co-authors%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nickname%20%26quot%3Bvampire%20stars%26quot%3B%20comes%20from%20the%20most%20accepted%20theory%20of%20how%20type-Be%20stars%20form%20rings%2C%20researchers%20said%20in%20the%20study%20%E2%80%94%20by%20sucking%20the%20metaphorical%20neck%20of%20an%20intergalactic%20victim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EType-Be%20stars%2C%20as%20they%20rapidly%20spin%2C%20collect%20matter%20from%20a%20companion%20star%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farstechnica.com%2Fscience%2F2022%2F03%2Fstudy-theres-no-black-hole-in-this-vampire-binary-star-system-after-all%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etheory%3C%2Fa%3E%20says.%20This%20matter%20then%20surrounds%20the%20star%20as%20a%20ring%20and%20causes%20the%20type-Be%20star%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Espin%20faster%20as%20it%20accumulates%20more%20from%20its%20companion.%20These%20companions%2C%20which%20become%20even%20smaller%20due%20to%20the%20loss%20of%20matter%2C%20can%20be%20anything%20from%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D5e07e11bb81cd00e6ad0d73504f6ea1fb8531016c63001b6dfddf887d1d6db5a%26postID%3D6562e777c49e08a1734a9194%26postSlug%3Dtype-be-vampire-stars-secret-helper-2023-11%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.nature.com%252Farticles%252Fnature12916%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eneutron%20star%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fabs%2F2304.02615%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhite%20dwarf.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20they%20began%20the%20process%20of%20rapidly%20rotating%20and%20collecting%20matter%2C%20however%2C%20was%20a%20mystery.%20Regular%20type-B%20stars%20also%20had%20companions%20they%20weren't%20feasting%20upon%2C%20so%20what%20made%20the%20two%20different%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20blue%20star%20stealing%20material%20from%20a%20smaller%20blue%20star%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656663fafe5bc6545ebd262b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221778%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EArtist's%20impression%20of%20a%20vampire%20star%20(left)%20stealing%20material%20from%20its%20victim%3Cp%3EESO%2FM.%20Kornmesser%2FS.E.%20de%20Mink%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20say%20a%20heretofore%20unobserved%20third%20star%20is%20likely%20facilitating%20the%20mass%20transfer%20by%20bringing%20the%20type-Be%20star%20and%20its%20companion%20closer%20together%2C%20just%20as%20a%20vampire's%20thrall%20could%20lead%20a%20victim%20to%20its%20master.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20go%20into%20the%20study%20thinking%20that%20we%20would%20find%20triples%2C%20rather%20we%20went%20in%20looking%20for%20how%20often%20these%20stars%20were%20in%20doubles%2C%20but%20based%20on%20our%20results%2C%20triples%20ended%20up%20being%20the%20most%20reasonable%20explanation%20for%20what%20we%20were%20seeing%2C%26quot%3B%20Dodd%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'Triples%20are%20the%20new%20doubles'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20University%20of%20Leeds%20scientists%20used%20data%20from%20European%20Space%20Agency%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fastronomers-discover-fastest-runaway-stars-in-milky-way-galaxy-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esatellites%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cosmos.esa.int%2Fweb%2Fhipparcos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHipparcos%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.esa.int%2FScience_Exploration%2FSpace_Science%2FGaia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGaia%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20to%20map%20out%20the%20universe's%20stars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20observed%20the%20type-Be%20stars%20by%20comparing%20the%20positions%20of%20various%20stars%20over%20longer%20and%20shorter%20periods.%20The%20team%20also%20looked%20at%20type-B%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Estars%20to%20compare%20the%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20said%20that%20if%20the%20positions%20of%20the%20stars%20moved%20in%20a%20straight%20line%2C%20there%20was%20only%20one%20star%20in%20the%20system.%20If%20it%20wobbled%20or%20spiraled%2C%20one%20of%20the%20stars%20had%20a%20companion%20star.%20This%20is%20because%20gravitational%20forces%20influence%20the%20movement%20of%20the%20star.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20team%20was%20surprised%20to%20learn%20that%20they%20were%20detecting%20a%20higher%20rate%20of%20binary%20systems%20for%20type-B%20stars%20than%20for%20type-Be%20stars.%20Additionally%2C%20when%20researchers%20did%20find%20companions%20for%20the%20type-Be%20stars%2C%20the%20distances%20between%20their%20companions%20and%20those%20of%20the%20type-B%20stars%20%E2%80%94%20which%20do%20not%20have%20the%20characteristic%20rings%20%E2%80%94%20were%20fairly%20similar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20then%20expanded%20their%20search%20to%20see%20if%20the%20type-Be%20stars%20may%20have%20had%20companions%20at%20further%20distances.%20That's%20when%20the%20rate%20of%20companions%20began%20to%20even%20out%20between%20the%20type-B%20and%20type-Be%20stars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20led%20researchers%20to%20believe%20the%20distant%20companion%20they%20observed%20with%20the%20type-Be%20stars%20was%20actually%20the%20third%20star.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20three-star%20systems%20are%20inherently%20unstable%2C%20the%20stars%2C%20which%20begin%20close%20together%2C%20eventually%20eject%20one%20star.%20The%20force%20of%20the%20third%20star%20quickly%20ejecting%20from%20the%20group%20can%20pull%20the%20type-Be%20star%20and%20its%20companion%20star%20close%20together%20to%20commence%20the%20feeding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDodd%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20this%20phenomenon%20is%20most%20common%20in%20other%20triple-star%20systems%2C%20which%20also%20lent%2