onal%20market%20drivers%20like%20earnings%20growth%20and%20valuations.%20In%20a%20note%20this%20week%2C%20Bank%20of%20America%20strategists%20Joseph%20Quinlan%20and%20Lauren%20Sanfilippo%20broke%20down%20the%20five%20biggest%20lessons%20of%20the%20year%20as%20markets%20get%20ready%20to%20turn%20the%20calendar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20lesson%3F%20%26quot%3BDon't%20bet%20against%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analysts%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20year%20ago%2C%20most%20forecasters%20expected%20a%20recession%20in%202023%20thanks%20to%20the%20Federal%20Reserve's%20aggressive%20monetary%20policy%20tightening.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20instead%20of%20rolling%20over%2C%20the%20economy%20pushed%20forward%2C%20with%20strong%20consumer%20spending%20and%20a%20robust%20labor%20market%20powering%20growth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US%20economy%20is%20still%20the%20greatest%20show%20on%20planet%20Earth%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20strategists%20said.%20They%20described%20the%20country%20as%20a%20%2427%20trillion%20%26quot%3Bhydra-headed%20behemoth%26quot%3B%20that%20is%20the%20best%20at%20many%20different%20economic%20activities%20including%20agriculture%2C%20aerospace%2C%20energy%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20takeaway%2C%20according%20to%20the%20bank%2C%20is%20that%20China%20needs%20a%20new%20growth%20model.%20The%20much-hyped%20post-pandemic%20rebound%20never%20arrived%2C%20and%20instead%20the%20world's%20second%20largest%20economy%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-deflation-markets-property-real-estate-housing-beijing-2023-8%5C%22%3Esaddled%20with%20an%20ailing%20property%20sector%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-housing-market-economy-japan-jpmorgan-financial-investors-geopolitics-demographics-2023-8%5C%22%3Eaging%20demographics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20declining%20foreign%20investment%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20poi