%20chal%20raha%20hai%2C%20inke%20aaqa%20hai%20wahan%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%A6%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAgar%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0vote%C2%A0%3Cem%3Edena%20hai%2C%20agar%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EHindustan%3Cem%3E%C2%A0me%20rehna%20hai%2C%20toh%20mai%20kehta%20hoon%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0Modi%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eaur%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EYogi%3Cem%3E%2C%20ye%20do%20hain%2C%20aur%20aapke%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThackeray.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(%E2%80%98They%20operate%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20this%20is%20what%20the%20media%20of%20the%20country%20is%20showing%2C%20they%20have%20found%20out%2C%20they%20know%20everything%2C%20their%20leaders%20are%20there%E2%80%A6%20If%20you%20want%20to%20vote%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20live%20in%20India%2C%20then%20I%20say%2C%20Modi%20and%20Yogi%2C%20these%20are%20the%20two%2C%20and%20your%20Thackeray%E2%80%99.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20Chaudhary%20was%20booked%20under%20Section%20302%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20for%20murder%2C%20along%20with%20sections%20of%20the%20Arms%20Act%20and%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701524387000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F03005229%2FF2YFcpNWwAEWXWa.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Frpf-constable-who-killed-four-on-moving-train-wants-to-donate-to-ayodhya-ram-temple%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chetan%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20in%20jail%2C%20wants%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20court%20through%20his%20lawyers%20to%20de-freeze%20his%20bank%20account%20so%20that%20he%20can%20contribute%20to%20the%20temple.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Frpf-constable-who-killed-four-on-moving-train-wants-to-donate-to-ayodhya-ram-temple%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20Recalls%20Negotiation%20Team%20From%20Qatar%20After%20Dead%20End%20In%20Hostage%20Talks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsrael%20and%20Hamas%20brushed%20off%20international%20calls%20to%20renew%20an%20expired%20truce%20Saturday%20as%20air%20strikes%20pounded%20targets%20in%20Gaza%20and%20Palestinian%20groups%20launched%20volleys%20of%20rockets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmoke%20again%20clouded%20the%20sky%20over%20the%20north%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20territory%2C%20whose%20Hamas%20government%20said%20240%20people%20had%20been%20killed%20since%20a%20pause%20in%20hostilities%20expired%20early%20Friday%20and%20combat%20resumed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Israel%2C%20the%20military's%20Home%20Front%20Command%20reported%2040%20missile%20alerts%20in%20the%20south%20and%20centre%20of%20the%20country%2C%20and%20the%20Palestinian%20groups%20Hamas%20and%20Islamic%20Jihad%20announced%20%26quot%3Brocket%20barrages%26quot%3B%20against%20three%20Israeli%20municipalities%20near%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20an%20estimated%201.7%20million%20people%20in%20Gaza%20--%20around%2080%20percent%20of%20the%20population%20--%20have%20been%20displaced%20by%20eight%20weeks%20of%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFadel%20Naim%2C%20chief%20doctor%20at%20the%20Al-Ahli%20Arab%20Hospital%20in%20Gaza%20City%2C%20said%20his%20morgue%20had%20received%2030%20bodies%20since%20the%20morning%2C%20including%20seven%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20planes%20bombed%20our%20houses%3A%20three%20bombs%2C%20three%20houses%20destroyed%2C%26quot%3B%20Nemr%20al-Bel%2C%2043%2C%20told%20AFP%2C%20adding%20he%20had%20counted%2010%20dead%20in%20his%20family%20and%20%26quot%3B13%20more%20still%20under%20the%20rubble%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20population%20is%20short%20of%20food%2C%20water%20and%20other%20essentials%2C%20and%20many%20homes%20have%20been%20destroyed.%20UN%20agencies%20have%20declared%20a%20humanitarian%20catastrophe%2C%20although%20some%20aid%20trucks%20did%20arrive%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20truce%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20expired%20on%20Friday%2C%20Israel%20had%20told%20NGOs%20not%20to%20bring%20aid%20convoys%20across%20the%20Rafah%20border%20crossing%20from%20Egypt%2C%20the%20Palestine%20Red%20Crescent%20Society%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20Saturday%2C%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post%2C%20the%20charity%20said%20its%20Egyptian%20colleagues%20had%20managed%20to%20send%20over%20a%20number%20of%20trucks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20sides%20blamed%20each%20other%20for%20the%20breakdown%20of%20the%20truce%2C%20which%20had%20enabled%20the%20release%20of%2080%20Israeli%20hostages%20in%20exchange%20for%20240%20Palestinian%20prisoners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20truce%20had%20been%20brokered%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Qatar%2C%20backed%20by%20Egypt%20and%20the%20United%20States%2C%20but%20on%20Saturday%20Israel%20said%20it%20was%20withdrawing%20its%20negotiators%20from%20Doha%20after%20reaching%20a%20dead%20end%20in%20talks%20aimed%20at%20securing%20a%20renewed%20pause%20in%20hostilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFollowing%20the%20impasse%20in%20the%20negotiations%20and%20at%20the%20direction%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20David%20Barnea%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Mossad%2C%20ordered%20his%20team%20in%20Doha%20to%20return%20to%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Israeli%20leader's%20office%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrench%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20appealed%20for%20%26quot%3Bstepped-up%20efforts%20to%20reach%20a%20lasting%20ceasefire%26quot%3B%20to%20free%20all%20hostages%2C%20allow%20in%20more%20aid%20and%20to%20assure%20Israel%20of%20its%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20unprecedented%20attack%20on%20October%207%2C%20Hamas%20fighters%20broke%20through%20Gaza's%20militarised%20border%20into%20Israel%2C%20killed%20about%201%2C200%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20and%20took%20around%20240%20Israelis%20and%20foreigners%20hostage%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20vowed%20to%20eliminate%20Hamas%20in%20response%20and%20unleashed%20an%20air%20and%20ground%20campaign%20that%20has%20killed%20more%20than%2015%2C000%20people%2C%20also%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20the%20Hamas%20authorities%20who%20run%20Gaza%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20end%20of%20the%20pause%2C%20Israel's%20air%2C%20naval%20and%20ground%20forces%20have%20attacked%20more%20than%20400%20targets%20in%20Gaza%2C%20the%20army%20said%20on%20Saturday.%20The%20figure%20is%20roughly%20in%20line%20with%20the%20daily%20average%20number%20of%20strikes%20prior%20to%20the%20pause%2C%20according%20to%20military%20figures%20released%20previously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWarplanes%20hit%20%26quot%3Bmore%20than%2050%20targets%20in%20an%20extensive%20attack%20in%20the%20Khan%20Yunis%20area%26quot%3B%20of%20Gaza's%20south%2C%20the%20military%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20members%20of%20an%20Israeli%20armoured%20brigade%20%26quot%3Beliminated%20terrorist%20squads%20and%20directed%20fire%20against%20terrorist%20targets%20in%20the%20north%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20military%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20truce%20expired%2C%20Hamas%C2%A0has%20fired%20rockets%20from%20Gaza%20towards%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternational%20leaders%20and%20humanitarian%20groups%20condemned%20the%20return%20to%20fighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20deeply%20regret%20that%20military%20operations%20have%20started%20again%20in%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20UN%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20said%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFighting%20also%20resumed%20on%20Israel's%20northern%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lebanese%20group%20Hezbollah%2C%20which%20like%20Hamas%20is%20backed%20by%20Iran%2C%20said%20two%20of%20its%20members%20were%20killed%20Friday%20in%20Israeli%20strikes%20on%20Lebanon%2C%20as%20its%20fighters%20resumed%20attacks%20against%20Israeli%20targets%20following%20the%20end%20of%20the%20truce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20said%20its%20artillery%20struck%20the%20sources%20of%20%26quot%3Blaunches%26quot%3B%20from%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESyria%20said%20Israel%20carried%20out%20air%20strikes%20near%20Damascus%20on%20Saturday.%20A%20British-based%20war%20monitor%20said%20the%20strikes%20on%20%26quot%3BHezbollah%20sites%26quot%3B%20killed%20two%20Syrian%20pro-Hezbollah%20fighters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran's%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20accused%20Israel%20of%20killing%20two%20of%20its%20members%20in%20Syria%20who%20it%20said%20had%20been%20on%20an%20%26quot%3Badvisory%20mission%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20in%20October%20last%20year%20said%20it%20had%20restored%20relations%20with%20Syria's%20government.%20Israeli%20attacks%20on%20targets%20in%20Syria%20have%20intensified%20since%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20week%20of%20hostage-prisoner%20exchanges%20yielded%20tearful%20reunions%20of%20Israeli%20families%20with%20their%20released%20relatives%20and%20jubilation%20in%20the%20streets%20of%20the%20Israeli-occupied%20West%20Bank%20as%20Palestinians%20walked%20free%20from%20Israeli%20jails.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty-five%20other%20hostages%2C%20mostly%20Thais%2C%20were%20also%20freed%20in%20separate%20arrangements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20army%20on%20Friday%20said%20136%20hostages%20were%20still%20being%20held%20in%20Gaza%2C%20including%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20end%20of%20the%20pause%20meant%20bitter%20disappointment%20for%20the%20families%20of%20those%20still%20not%20freed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20a%20chance%20for%20people%20to%20come%20out%2C%20be%20reunited%20with%20their%20families%20and%20resume%20their%20old%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ilan%20Zharia%2C%20the%20uncle%20of%20Eden%20Yerushalmi%2C%2020%2C%20one%20of%20the%20women%20still%20held%20captive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERomania%20said%20it%20had%20been%20told%20by%20Israel%20that%20a%20Romanian-Israeli%20hostage%20had%20died%20in%20Gaza.%3C%