%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Avrocar%20may%20look%20like%20a%20flying%20saucer%20from%20a%20sci-fi%20movie%2C%20but%20it%20was%20intended%20for%20practical%20purposes.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222940%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20the%20circular%20Avrocar%20aircraft%20from%20above.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6568f56547f9ecb37d88da02%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Avrocar%20is%20being%20rolled%20out%20for%20one%20of%20its%20initial%20test%20flights.%3Cp%3EUS%20National%20Archives%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20Air%20Force%20wanted%20an%20aircraft%20that%20could%20take%20off%20vertically%2C%20fly%20under%20radar%20scans%2C%20and%20intercept%20enemy%20ships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitial%20designs%20for%20the%20plane%20promised%20that%20it%20would%20be%20able%20to%20achieve%20speeds%20three%20times%20the%20speed%20of%20sound%2C%20thus%20creating%20the%20supersonic%20fighter%20bomber%20the%20Canadians%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20circular%20design%20of%20the%20ship%20was%20more%20than%20an%20aesthetic%20choice.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222940%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20men%20stand%20on%20opposite%20sides%20of%20a%20wooden%20half-circle%20that%20would%20become%20the%20inner%20skeleton%20of%20the%20to-scale%20model%20of%20the%20Avrocar.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6568f68e58e7c0c29a287c62%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwo%20engineers%20work%20on%20a%20wooden%20skeleton%20for%20a%20to-scale%20model%20of%20the%20Avrocar.%3Cp%3EUnited%20States%20National%20Archives%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Carver%20%26quot%3BJack%26quot%3B%20Frost%20was%20a%20respected%20aircraft%20designer%20who%20aimed%20to%20leverage%20the%20Coanda%20effect%20to%20benefit%20a%20circular%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20circular%2