n-threat-humanity-2023-11%5C%22%3Ethe%20OpenAI%20management%20fiasco%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Huang%20simply%20is%20not%20concerned%20about%20a%20doomsday%20scenario%20related%20to%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20AI%20might%20someday%20kill%20somebody%2C%20one%20Nvidia%20executive%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEh%2C%20electricity%20kills%20people%20every%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20question%20posed%20was%20whether%20AI%20might%20become%20self-aware%20one%20day%2C%20but%20Huang%20wasn't%20buying%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20order%20for%20you%20to%20be%20a%20creature%2C%20you%20have%20to%20be%20conscious.%20You%20have%20to%20have%20some%20knowledge%20of%20self%2C%20right%3F%20I%20don't%20know%20where%20that%20could%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E5.%20Huang%20encourages%20employees%20to%20develop%20products%20for%20%26quot%3Bzero-billion-dollar%20markets%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20bulk%20of%20Nvidia's%20success%20can%20be%20chalked%20up%20to%20the%20company%20skating%20to%20where%20the%20puck%20is%20going%2C%20years%20in%20advance.%20And%20Huang%20encourages%20that%20level%20of%20thinking%20as%20its%20employees%20develop%20new%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20calls%20it%20the%20%26quot%3Bzero-billion-dollar%20market.%26quot%3B%20These%20exploratory%20products%20might%20not%20have%20competitors%20or%20even%20potential%20customers%20today%2C%20but%20that%20could%20change%20years%20down%20the%20road.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20compared%20this%20idea%20of%20thinking%20to%20the%20movie%20%26quot%3BField%20of%20Dreams%26quot%3B%2C%20in%20which%20the%20main%20character%20builds%20a%20baseball%20field%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20cornfield%2C%20then%20waits%20for%20players%20and%20fans%20to%20come%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E6.%20Huang's%20big%20gamble%20on%20the%20future%20is%20the%20Omniverse%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20took%20big%20risks%20over%20the%20past%20few%20decades%2C%20bett