ar-old%20victim%20in%20a%20fictitious%20money-laundering%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20case%20was%20recently%20reported%20in%20Haryana's%20Faridabad%20where%20cyber%20thugs%2C%20posing%20as%20police%20personnel%2C%20got%20a%20woman%20%26quot%3Bdigitally%20arrested%26quot%3B%20for%20more%20than%20a%20week%20after%20convincing%20her%20that%20her%20personal%20IDs%20were%20used%20for%20illegal%20activities.%20The%20thugs%20then%20asked%20her%20to%20stay%20online%20via%20Skype%20and%20not%20share%20this%20information%20with%20anyone%20even%20as%20they%20kept%20a%20watch%20on%20her%20throughout%20the%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20complaint%2C%20the%20Noida-based%20woman%20has%20claimed%20that%20she%20was%20contacted%20over%20an%20IVR%20(interactive%20voice%20response)%20call%20on%20November%2013%20and%20told%20that%20a%20mobile%20phone%20SIM%20card%20was%20purchased%20using%20her%20Aadhaar%20card%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20used%20for%20illegal%20advertising%20and%20harassment%20of%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20my%20call%20was%20transferred%20to%20a%20person%20(who%20identified%20himself%20as%20a%20Mumbai%20Police%20officer)%20who%20did%20the%20initial%20interrogation%20over%20the%20call%20and%20then%20on%20Skype%20VC.%20Then%20he%20informed%20that%20I%20have%20another%20allegation%20of%20money%20laundering%20related%20to%20(the%20founder%20of%20an%20airline)%20for%20which%20an%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20me%20and%20an%20arrest%20warrant%20issued%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20which%20he%20sent%20documents%20on%20Skype%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20woman%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20interrogation%2C%20he%20said%20I%20am%20innocent%20and%20not%20guilty%2C%20so%20he%20is%20transferring%20the%20interrogation%20(to%20an%20IPS%20officer%20posted%20with%20the%20CBI%2C%20Mumbai)%20for%20further%20investigation%20of%20this%20case.%20Then%20he%20gave%20the%20Skype%20ID%20and%20asked%20me%20to%20request%20the%20CBI%20officer%20to%20do%20the%20priority%20investigation%20on%20VC%20to%20remove%20my%20arrest%20warrant%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20has%20said%20in%20her%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20said%20CBI%20officer%20told%20her%20that%20during%20the%20investigation%20of%20the%20airline%20founder%2C%20police%20found%20246%20debit%20cards%20from%20his%20house%20and%20one%20of%20those%20had%20the%20victim's%20name%20on%20it%2C%20which%20was%20used%20to%20open%20a%20bank%20account%20with%20her%20Aadhaar%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20then%20said%20my%20account%20was%20used%20for%20a%20fund%20transfer%20of%20Rs%202%20crore%20for%20which%20I%20have%20been%20paid%20Rs%2020%20lakh.%20However%2C%20he%20said%20I%20do%20not%20look%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20this%20case%2C%20so%20to%20complete%20the%20investigation%2C%20I%20need%20to%20transfer%20funds%20from%20all%20my%20accounts%20to%20my%20ICICI%20account%20and%20subsequently%2C%20transfer%20the%20funds%20from%20the%20ICICI%20account%20to%20the%20PFC%20account%20as%20per%20the%20directives%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court...%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20has%20claimed%20that%20she%20was%20told%20not%20to%20disclose%20this%20information%20as%20it%20was%20related%20to%20%26quot%3Bnational%20security%20and%20will%20make%20me%20liable%20for%20further%20action%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlso%2C%20to%20prove%20not%20guilty%20of%20the%20crime%2C%20he%20asked%20me%20to%20keep%20sufficient%20balance%20in%20my%20accounts%20for%20which%20he%20also%20advised%20to%20apply%20for%20a%20personal%20instant%20loan%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20from%20ICICI%20and%20gave%20the%20details%20of%20how%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20same%2C%20which%20I%20denied%20but%20he%20forced%20me%20to%20arrange%20Rs%203%20lakh%20more%20through%20the%20same%20and%20after%20much%20pressure%2C%20I%20had%20applied%20for%20the%20same%2C%20which%20is%20also%20transferred%20to%20the%20PFC%20account%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20also%20took%20a%20picture%20of%20my%20signature%20on%20Skype%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20validating%20my%20Aadhaar%20card%20for%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20has%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20reported%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Police's%20Cyber%20Crime%20officials%20and%20alleged%20a%20fraud%20of%20Rs%2011.11%20lakh%20with%20her%2C%20besides%20being%20%26quot%3Bdigitally%20arrested%26quot%3B%20from%20morning%20to%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspector%20Reeta%20Yadav%2C%20in-charge%20of%20the%20Cyber%20Crime%20police%20station%20in%20Noida%20Sector%2036%2C%20said%20an%20FIR%20has%20been%20lodged%20under%20the%20relevant%20provisions%20of%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act%20and%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20investigation%20into%20the%20case%20is%20underway%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20urged%20people%20to%20be%20cautious%20of%20emerging%20online%20crimes%20and%20reach%20out%20to%20police%20at%20the%20earliest%20either%20on%20the%20central%20helpline%20number%201930%20or%20emergency%20number%20112%20or%20report%20such%20activities%20to%20the%20cyber%20desk%20of%20local%20police%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20should%20also%20know%20that%20police%20never%20question%20any%20person%20digitally.%20If%20someone%20threatens%20you%20like%20this%2C%20ask%20them%20to%20send%20you%20a%20proper%20notice%2C%20ask%20for%20their%20details%20and%20tell%20them%20that%20you%20are%20coming%20to%20the%20police%20station%20to%20meet%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701523140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-09%2Fcyber-crime-generic-istock_650x400_81504427706.jp