C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20dealt%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20bullying%2C%20depression%2C%20and%20anxiety%20as%20a%20child.%20For%20a%20while%2C%20that%20dream%20just%20kind%20of%20faded%20into%20the%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20born%20in%20the%20United%20States%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0my%20dad%20is%20from%20Pennsylvania%20and%20my%20mom%20is%20Nepali%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20grew%20up%20there%20until%20the%20age%20of%2010.%20Then%20my%20parents%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20Nepal%2C%20and%20I've%20lived%20there%20for%20the%20past%2013%20years.%20I%20went%20to%20an%20international%20school%20and%20was%20very%20isolated.%20I%20didn't%20have%20many%20people%20skills%20and%20struggled%20with%20mental%20health%20problems.%20I%20started%20self-harming%20at%20the%20age%20of%2016.%20I%20starved%20myself%2C%20I%20had%20anorexia%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0it%20was%20a%20really%20hard%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20also%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20hormonal%20problems%20throughout%20my%20life%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20know%20what%20was%20going%20on%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20I%20always%20had%20irregular%20periods%2C%20mood%20swings%2C%20depression%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20body%20hair%2C%20and%20I%20would%20gain%20weight%20very%20easily.%20It%20made%20me%20feel%20insecure%20about%20myself.%20I%20would%20compare%20myself%20to%20other%20girls%20and%20feel%20like%20I%20wasn't%20skinny%20enough.%20But%20I%20would%20go%20to%20the%20doctor%20and%20they%20would%20say%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20that's%20normal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Miss%20Nepal%202023%20Jane%20Garrett%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656a1c0c86933e8fdb2ee265%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGarrett%20during%20the%20Miss%20Universe%20competition%20in%20San%20Salvador%2C%20El%20Salvador.%3Cp%3EHector%20Vivas%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20lockdown%2C%20I%20gained%2030%20pounds%20and%20had%20severe%20health%20problems.%20My%20partner%20made%20me%20go%20to%20the%20doctor%20and%20they%20found%20out%20I%20had%20extremely%20large%20cysts%20in%20my%20ovaries.%20I%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20polycystic%20ovary%20syndrome%20(PCOS)%20and%20borderline%20personality%20disorder%2C%20which%20is%20directly%20linked%20to%20PCOS.%20It's%20a%20hormonal%20imbalance%20as%20well%20as%20a%20mental%20health%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20year%20ago%20I%20attempted%20to%20end%20my%20own%20life%2C%20but%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20a%20higher%20power.%20He%20told%20me%20I%20have%20a%20purpose%20in%20life%2C%20that%20there's%20a%20reason%20why%20I'm%20alive%2C%20and%20I'm%20here%20to%20inspire%20millions%20of%20people%20around%20the%20world%20to%20love%20themselves.%20Ever%20since%20then%2C%20I've%20transformed%20my%20entire%20life.%20It%20was%20a%20breaking%20point%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20to%20compare%20myself%20to%20others.%20But%20now%20I%20love%20my%20body%2C%20I%20love%20it%20so%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20in%20nursing%20school%20at%20the%20time%20and%2C%20instead%20of%20quitting%2C%20I%20graduated.%20Then%20I%20saw%20the%20Miss%20Universe%20Nepal%20application%20was%20open%20and%20I%20was%20inspired%20to%20try%20it.%20I%20thought%20it%20could%20be%20a%20stepping%20stone%20for%20me.%20I%20didn't%20think%20I%20would%20win%2C%20I%20just%20joined%20to%20gain%20experience%20and%20confidence.%20I%20embraced%20myself%20and%20I%20was%20there%20for%20a%20purpose%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0to%20represent%20real-sized%20beauty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20I%20ended%20up%20winning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Miss%20Nepal%202023%20Jane%20Garrett%20during%20the%20Miss%20Universe%20swimsuit%20competition%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656a1d3258e7c0c29a28cd44%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGarrett%20during%20the%20swimsuit%20competition%20at%20Miss%20Universe.%3Cp%3EMARVIN%20RECINOS%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBecoming%20Miss%20Nepal%20felt%20amazing.%20I%20didn't%20go%20there%20to%20become%20the%20first%20plus-sized%20woman%20to%20win%20Miss%20Nepal%2C%20I%20went%20there%20as%20myself%20and%20as%20a%20person.%20But%20it%20also%20felt%20really%20good%20to%20be%20a%20curvy%20woman%2C%20a%20plus-sized%20woman%2C%20to%20win%20and%20represent%20all%20these%20women%20around%20the%20world.%20It%20was%20a%20trailblazing%20moment%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20prepared%20hard%20for%20the%20Miss%20Universe%20competition%2C%20and%20my%20goal%20was%20to%20win%20and%20represent%20real-sized%20women%20everywhere.%20I%20was%20working%20about%2016%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20doing%20walk%20training%2C%20talk%20training%2C%20and%20interview%20training.%20I%20was%20organizing%20all%20my%20outfits%20on%20my%20own%2C%20working%20out%2C%20and%20preparing%20myself%20mentally%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiss%20Universe%20was%20wild%2C%20it%20was%20overwhelming%2C%20and%20I%20loved%20it.%20My%20favorite%20part%20was%20interacting%20with%20all%20the%20girls%20from%20all%20the%20different%20countries.%20I%20got%20to%20experience%20so%20many%20different%20cultures%2C%20I%20got%20to%20experience%20El%20Salvador%20and%20the%20wonderful%20people%20there%2C%20and%20just%20be%20in%20the%20moment%20and%20be%20present.%20It%20wasn't%20just%20about%20the%20competition%2C%20it%20was%20about%20experiencing%20this%20whole%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20heard%20my%20name%20called%20in%20the%20top%2020%2C%20it%20felt%20really%20good.%20I%20felt%20very%20empowered%20and%20like%20I%20was%20changing%20society's%20standards.%20During%20the%20swimsuit%20competition%2C%20I%20got%20the%20biggest%20applause%20and%20I%20felt%20so%20supported%20by%20the%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20afraid%20to%20discuss%20my%20mental%20health%20and%20hormonal%20issues%20at%20Miss%20Univers