s%20to%20join%20the%20peace%20process%20so%20that%20a%20solution%20towards%20peace%20can%20be%20brought%20to%20Manipur.%20The%20UNLF%20is%20a%2060%20years%20old%20organisation%20that%20never%20agreed%20to%20talk%2C%20but%20this%20time%20they%20have%20reposed%20faith%20in%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20ji%2C%20so%20it's%20a%20major%20achievement%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UNLF%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipurs-oldest-armed-group-unlf-signs-peace-deal-with-centre-4617628%5C%22%3Ehad%20been%20fighting%20a%20guerilla%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20sovereign%20Manipur%20as%20the%20group%20-%20similar%20to%20other%20valley-based%20banned%20organisations%20like%20the%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20(PLA)%20-%20considered%20illegal%20the%20merger%20of%20the%20pre-Independence%20Manipur%20kingdom%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUNLF%20general%20secretary%20Ch%20Thanil%20said%20they%20are%20happy%20to%20join%20the%20peace%20process%20and%20will%20do%20everything%20to%20ensure%20lasting%20stability.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20talk%20peacefully%20and%20if%20the%20amicable%20solution%20comes%2C%20we%20will%20sign%20the%20final%20deal...%20The%20present%20crisis%20is%20a%20very%20small%20matter.%20Actually%2C%20some%20people%20from%20outside%20have%20been%20behind%20this%20disturbance%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thanil%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20recent%20ethnic%20clashes%20between%20the%20hill-majority%20Kuki%20tribes%20and%20the%20valley-majority%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20express%20my%20sincere%20gratitude%20to%20UNLF%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20and%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur%20for%20their%20unwavering%20support%20throughout%20this%20transformative%20journey.%20Let%20this%20be%20a%20moment%20of%20renewed%20hope%2C%20where%20bridges%20are%20built%2C%20and%20relationships%20are%20strengthened.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Foq12SE5Xzl%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Foq12SE5Xzl%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20N.Biren%20Singh%20(%40NBirenSingh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNBirenSingh%2Fstatus%2F1730893972628017558%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%202%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20descriptor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funlf-decoded-manipurs-oldest-valley-armed-groups-farewell-to-arms-explained-4620490%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bvalley-based%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20UNLF%3C%2Fa%3E%20indicates%20it%20was%20an%20armed%20group%20with%20origins%20in%20Imphal%20valley%20and%20other%20districts%20not%20classified%20as%20hill%20areas.%20Similarly%2C%20at%20least%2025%20hill-based%20insurgent%20groups%20are%20already%20under%20a%20tripartite%20peace%20deal%20called%20the%20suspension%20of%20operations%20(SoO)%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20express%20my%20sincere%20gratitude%20to%20UNLF%2C%20the%20government%20of%20India%2C%20and%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur%20for%20their%20unwavering%20support%20throughout%20this%20transformative%20journey.%20Let%20this%20be%20a%20moment%20of%20renewed%20hope%2C%20where%20bridges%20are%20built%2C%20and%20relationships%20are%20strengthened%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20faced%20criticism%20over%20the%20Manipur%20violence%2C%20and%20questions%20on%20how%20law%20and%20order%20could%20not%20be%20maintained.%20The%20peace%20deal%20with%20the%20UNLF%20-%20the%20first%20with%20any%20valley-based%20armed%20group%20-%20is%2C%20however%2C%20being%20seen%20as%20Mr%20Singh%20and%20the%20BJP's%20masterstroke%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20general%20election%20since%20it%20is%20for%20the%20first%20time%20that%20a%20valley-based%20armed%20group%20has%20agreed%20to%20lay%20down%20arms%20and%20join%20the%20mainstr