0the%20country%E2%80%99s%20most%20backward%20states%20with%20a%20high%20population%20of%20marginalised%20Hindu%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20him%20leading%20the%20charge%20as%20the%20main%20face%20of%20the%20campaign%2C%20overshadowing%20the%20outgoing%20chief%20minister%2C%20the%20result%20would%20also%2C%20to%20an%20extent%2C%20be%20a%20reflection%20on%20his%20leadership%20and%20popularity%2C%20although%20in%20case%20of%20an%20adverse%20result%20the%20BJP%20is%20expected%20to%20shield%20him%20from%20blame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03105424%2FScreenshot-2023-10-03-at-10.53.5.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03105424%2FScreenshot-2023-10-03-at-10.53.5.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03105424%2FScreenshot-2023-10-03-at-10.53.5-300x154.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F03105424%2FScreenshot-2023-10-03-at-10.53.5-1024x525.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-677981%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22615%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPM%20Narendra%20Modi%20at%20Gwalior%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20on%20October%202.%20Photo%3A%20Video%20screengrab%2FX%2F%40narendramodi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20strong%20anti-incumbency%20wave%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20hopes%20to%20repeat%2C%20or%20even%20better%20its%202018%20performance%2C%20when%20it%20won%20114%20seats%20in%20the%20230-member%20Assembly%2C%20the%20BJP%20faces%20the%20task%20of%20protecting%20one%20of%20its%20strongest%20political%20and%20ideological%20bastions%20in%20the%20entire%20country.%20Travelling%20in%20the%20state%2C%20beneath%20the%20maze%20of%20grievances%20and%20assertions%2C%20there%20were%20two%20dominant%20streams%20of%20thought%20among%20voters.%20There%20were%20those%20who%20appreciated%20the%20work%20done%20by%20the%20Chouhan-led%20BJP%20government%20since%202005%20and%20still%20trusted%20Modi%20as%20the%20supreme%20leader.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20long-standing%20link%20with%20Hindutva%20ideology%2C%20its%20organisational%20structure%2C%20welfare%20programs%2C%20particularly%20for%20women%2C%20financial%20support%2C%20and%20infrastructural%20development%20encouraged%20loyalty%20to%20the%20saffron%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatched%20against%20this%20was%20a%20solid%20and%20discernible%20sentiment%20of%20anti-incumbency%2C%20built%20on%20frustration%20over%20unemployment%2C%20inflation%2C%20unsatisfactory%20crop%20prices%2C%20repeated%20corruption%20allegations%2C%20scams%20obstructing%20recruitment%20to%20government%20jobs%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20boredom%20and%20fatigue%20with%20the%20way%20the%20state%20has%20been%20running%20under%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%2C%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20recognised%20its%20deficiencies%20as%20it%2C%20instead%20of%20selling%20the%20work%20done%20by%20it%20in%20the%20last%20tenure%2C%20desperately%20referred%20to%20the%20past%2C%20underlining%20the%20comparative%20change%20it%20brought%20about%20in%20the%20state%20over%20the%20two%20decades%20%E2%80%93%20the%20journey%20from%20%3Cem%3Ebimaru%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20%3Cem%3Ebemisaal%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-congress-has-an-edge-over-bjp-in-madhya-pradesh%5C%22%3EWhy%20Congress%20Has%20an%20Edge%20Over%20BJP%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20tribal%20dominated%20Dhar%20district%20in%20western%20MP%E2%80%99s%20Nimar%2C%20Phool%20Singh%2C%20a%20farmer%20who%20hails%20from%20the%20Bhilala%20tribe%2C%20was%20clear%20he%20wanted%20to%20give%20the%20Congress%20a%20chance%20to%20rule%20after%20two%20decades.%20The%20Congress%20promise%20of%20waiving%20off%20farm%20loans%2C%20reducing%20electricity%20bills%20and%20providing%20Rs%201%2C500%20stipend%20to%20women%20was%20a%20big%20catch%20in%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20dusty%20village%20in%20Manawar%20constituency.%20Sanju%2C%20a%20Bhilala%20woman%2C%20too%20wanted%20the%20Congress%20government%20as%20she%20felt%20that%20despite%20the%20long%20rule%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20educated%20youth%20in%20the%20state%20were%20unemployed.%20%E2%80%9CEveryone%20has%20changed%20sides%20in%20this%20election.%20So%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Raila%2C%20a%20Bhil%20farmer%2C%20who%20had%20previously%20supported%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20central%20MP%E2%80%99s%20Sehore%20district%2C%20Dalit%20farmer%20Sumer%20Singh%20fondly%20remembered%20the%20pre-2003%20Congress%20rule.%20He%20was%20unhappy%20with%20his%20stagnant%20standard%20of%20living%2C%20%E2%80%9Cendless%E2%80%9D%20inflation%20and%20rising%20costs%20of%20farming%2C%20uncertain%20rates%20for%20his%20%3Cem%3Etur%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20wheat%20crops%20and%20difficulty%20in%20procuring%20urea.%20%E2%80%9CEveryone%20is%20troubled%20by%20the%20BJP.%20Even%20the%20monsoon%20gods%20have%20stopped%20blessing%20us%20due%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20showcasing%20a%20hint%20of%20personal%20superstition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20substantial%20section%20of%20voters%20across%20caste%20and%20class%20expressed%20a%20negative%20sentiment%20against%20the%20Chouhan%20government%2C%20either%20based%20on%20fatigue%2C%20dissatisfaction%20or%20simply%20a%20desire%20for%20change%2C%20the%20saffron%20party%20still%20enjoyed%20a%20rock-solid%20base%20of%20committed%20voters%20in%20the%20central%20Indian%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09092514%2FF-aWeDnboAA_Tym.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09092514%2FF-aWeDnboAA_Tym.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09092514%2FF-aWeDnboAA_Tym-300x194.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09092514%2FF-aWeDnboAA_Tym-1024x662.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684198%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22776%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBJP%20supporters%20hold%20up%20Modi%20posters.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40narendramodi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20suppresses%20our%20Hindu%20brothers%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rahul%20Malviya%2C%20a%20driver%20in%20Sehore.%20When%20asked%20to%20count%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20provides%20us%20benefits%20from%20the%20moment%20we%20are%20born%20till%20we%20die.%20Then%20there%20is%20free%20ration.%20They%20also%20abrogated%20Article%20370%20%5Bin%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%5D%20and%20built%20the%20Ram%20Mandir.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Sagar%2C%20an%20OBC%20labourer%20Bharat%20Patel%2C%20though%20unsatisfied%20with%20the%20state%20government%2C%20felt%20he%20was%20obliged%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20Modi%20because%20of%20what%20they%20stood%20for.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20big%20discussion%20in%20my%20area%20about%20changing%20the%20government.%20I%E2%80%99m%20confused.%20My%20%3Cem%3Eaatma%3C%2Fem%3E%20(conscience)%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20allow%20me%20to%20vote%20against%20the%20BJP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20even%20though%20the%20BJP%20lost%20the%20election%20to%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20the%20BJP%20won%20109%20seats%20against%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20114%20%E2%80%93%20it%20secured%200.13%25%20more%20votes%2C%20showcasing%20its%20popular%20acceptance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20four%20elections%20in%20MP%20(2003%2C%202008%2C%202013%20and%202018)%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share%20in%20the%20state%20has%20been%2043%25%2C%2038%25%2C%2045%25%20and%2041%25%20as%20against%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%2032%25%2C%2032%25%2C%2036%25%20and%2041%25.%20Although%20the%20saffron%20party%20has%20occupied%20the%20dominant%20position%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20made%20consistent%20improvement%20which%20culminated%20in%20a%20remarkable%20jump%20in%202018%20when%20it%20formed%20government%20with%20the%20support%20of%20three%20opposition%20party%20MLAs%20and%20four%20independent%20legislators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20significant%20aspect%20of%20the%202018%20elections%20was%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20six%20percent%20vote%20share%20increase%20in%20the%20BJP-favoured%20territories%20of%20Madhya%20Bharat%20and%20Malwa%20North%2C%20noted%20political%20analyst%20Ashish%20Ranjan%20of%20%3Cem%3EDatalok.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20a%20recent%20report.%20This%20gain%20translated%20into%2020%20additional%20seats%20for%20the%20Congress%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20election%2C%20indicating%20a%20deep%20incision%20into%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20stronghold%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20run%20by%20Kamal%20Nath%20could%20only%20last%2015%20months%20after%20the%20BJP%20engineered%20mass%20defections%20in%20the%20Congress%20and%20snatched%20the%20reins%20from%20it%20in%202020.%20The%20defeat%20in%202018%20and%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20he%20returned%20to%20power%20in%202020%20had%20already%20reduced%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20stature.%20The%20way%20in%20which%20he%20was%20sidelined%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20its%20campaign%20%E2%80%93%20by%20not%20declaring%20him%20as%20the%20official%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20%E2%80%93%20has%20raised%20several%20questions%20on%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20political%20future.%20Whether%20the%20BJP%20loses%20or%20wins%2C%20the%20result%20day%20is%20a%20day%20of%20reckoning%20for%20him%20personally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EVM%20would%20not%20only%20settle%20the%20question%20whether%20Kamal%20Nath%20would%20get%20a%20second%20go%20at%20running%20a%20government%20but%20also%20provide%20us%20a%20glimpse%20of%20the%20battle%20for%20leadership%20within%20the%20BJP%20and%20how%20it%20approaches%20state%20elections%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20advantage%20of%20the%20BJP%20presenting%20a%20diverse%20front%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20fielding%20four%20MPs%2C%20three%20Union%20ministers%20%E2%80%93%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%2C%20Faggan%20Singh%20Kulaste%20and%20Prahlad%20Patel%20%E2%80%93%20and%20one%20national%20general%20secretary%20Kailash%20Vijayvargiya%20in%20the%20Assembly%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20opted%20for%20a%20fresh%20experiment%20of%20projecting%20a%20collective%20leadership%20under%20Modi.%20However%2C%20as%20the%20campaign%20took%20pace%20and%20his%20rivals%20got%20caught%20up%20in%20their%20respective%20constituencies%20and%20controversies%2C%20Chouhan%20tried%20hard%20to%20reclaim%20his%20position%20through%20extensive%20campaigning%20and%20showcasing%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20collective%20leadership%20gambit%20in%20a%20state%20where%20it%20already%20had%20a%20popular%20face%2C%20an%20OBC%20to%20boot%2C%20had%20several%20elements%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20it%20could%20be%20seen%20as%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20to%20provide%20options%20to%20voters%20disenchanted%20with%20Chouhan%20and%20looking%20for%20a%20fresh%20face%20to%20lead%20the%20government.%20Second%2C%20by%20fielding%20these%20leaders%2C%20who%20hail%20from%20different%20region%20and%20castes%2C%20the%20BJP%20sought%20to%20energise%20its%20cadre%20and%20tease%20voters%20across%20communities.%20This%20gave%20rise%20to%20the%20possibility%20that%20if%20the%20BJP%20won%2C%20it%20could%20provide%20a%20new%20chief%20minister%20from%20a%20particular%20caste.%20In%20a%20state%20with%20immense%20regional%20diversity%2C%20both%20politically%20and%20culturally%2C%20this%20tactic%2C%20in%20a%20tightly-fought%20battle%20could%20offset%20some%20loss%20or%20anti-incumbency.%20The%20third%20way%20of%20looking%20at%20the%20collective%20leadership%20was%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20diminishing%20stature%2C%20under%20whose%20leadership%20the%20BJP%20lost%20in%202018.%20A%20new%20chief%20minister%20could%20provide%20BJP%20a%20fresh%20outlook%20and%20agenda%20in%20the%20state%20where%20it%20already%20enjoys%20a%20strong%20organisational%20strength%20and%20ideological%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-bjps-hindutva-campaign-is-not-working-in-madhya-pradesh%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20Hindutva%20Card%20is%20Not%20Working%20for%20BJP%20in%20Poll-Bound%20Madhya%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20seized%20the%20initiative%20early-on%20as%20the%20saffron%20party%20trailed%20in%20the%20perception%20game%20for%20most%20of%20this%20year.%20The%20Congress%2C%20by%20causing%20defections%20of%20core%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20which%20coincided%20with%20a%20cloud%20of%20doubt%20hovering%20over%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20own%20future%2C%20appeared%20to%20be%20in%20the%20driving%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20declared%20a%20chief%20ministerial%20face%2C%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20and%20pursued%20its%20successful%20strategy%20of%20winning%20over%20voters%20in%20Karnataka%20through%20welfare%20guarantees%20and%20deliverables%20linked%20to%20social%20security.%20The%20party%20also%20did%20well%20to%20keep%20under%20wraps%20any%20signs%20of%20infighting%20and%20consistently%20projected%20a%20collective%20front%20under%20Nath%E2%80%99s%20leadership.%20The%20possible%20damage%20that%20the%20rebel%20candidates%20and%20disgruntled%20leaders%20may%20do%20to%20each%20party%2C%20and%20in%20particular%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20on%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20tally%2C%20would%20only%20be%20revealed%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFacing%20an%20early%20onslaught%20and%20a%20united%20Congress%2C%20Chouhan%20tried%20to%20project%20a%20counter%20narrative%20by%20launching%20schemes%20such%20as%20Ladli%20Behna%20to%20woo%20women%20voters%20through%20monetary%20benefits.%20While%20the%20Ladli%20Behna%20scheme%20appeared%20to%20be%20popular%2C%20it%20was%20not%20enough%20for%20everyone.%20For%20some%2C%20it%20came%20too%20late.%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9CThey%20started%20this%20scheme%20just%20a%20few%20months%20before%20the%20election.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20anything%20before%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rukmini%20Kushwaha%20in%20Indore.%20In%20a%20Dalit%20busty%20in%20Dewas%2C%20crippling%20inflation%20round-the-year%20and%20lack%20of%20overall%20improvement%20in%20life%20mattered%20more%20than%20monetary%20assistance.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20not%20received%20any%20toilet%20or%20%3Cem%3Epucca%3C%2Fem%3E%20house%20or%20water%20tank.%20Oil%20and%20tomatoes%20are%20priced%20like%20silver%20and%20gold%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Reena%2C%20a%20Dalit%20voter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20Congress%20promised%20to%20conduct%20a%20caste%20census%20if%20voted%20to%20power%2C%20the%20result%20would%20also%20provide%20opportunity%20to%20both%20parties%20to%20reflect%20on%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20counting%20of%20the%20OBC%20population%20in%20the%20build-up%20to%20the%20general%20election%20next%20year.%20However%2C%20on%20the%20surface%2C%20the%20caste%20census%20was%20not%20a%20big%20talking%20point%20among%20voters%2C%20with%20most%20of%20their%20concerns%20limited%20to%20livelihood%20issues%2C%20corruption%20and%20regional%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EJaisa%20chal%20raha%20hai%20chalne%20de%20sanatan%20dharm%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Let%20the%20Hindu%20faith%20and%20society%20function%20the%20way%20it%20is)%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kamal%20Rajak%2C%20an%20OBC%20farmer%20in%20Sagar%2C%20who%20despite%20wanting%20to%20change%20the%20government%20due%20to%20unemployment%2C%20believed%20a%20caste%20census%20would%20hurt%20the%20Hindu%20society.%20The%202023%20MP%20election%20result%20could%20possibly%20also%20impact%20the%20way%20the%20partners%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20deal%20with%20each%20other%20in%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20state%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20which%20has%2080%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigh-profile%20battle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20featured%20a%20number%20of%20high-profile%20and%20high-stake%20electoral%20battles%20involving%20top%20leaders%20from%20both%20parties%2C%20in%20particular%20the%20BJP%20which%20fielded%20several%20national-level%20heavyweights.In%20Budhni%2C%20Chouhan%20defended%20his%20fort%20against%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20Vikram%20Mastal%2C%20a%20TV%20actor-turned-politician%20known%20for%20playing%20the%20role%20of%20Hanuman%20in%20the%20serial%20Ramayan%20in%202008.%20Congress%20chief%20minsterial%20candidate%20Kamal%20Nath%20contested%20from%20Chhindwara%2C%20his%20political%20bastion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20leaders%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20also%20prospective%20chief%20minster%20candidates%2C%20were%20also%20in%20the%20fray%20this%20time.%20While%20Union%20agriculture%20minister%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%20contested%20from%20Dimni%20against%20the%20sitting%20Congress%20MLA%20Ravindra%20Singh%20Tomar%20Bhidosa%2C%20another%20important%20Union%20minister%2C%20Prahlad%20Singh%20Patel%2C%20was%20fielded%20from%20Narsingpur%20constituency%20where%20he%20replaced%20the%20sitting%20MLA%20and%20his%20younger%20brother%20Jalam%20Singh%20Patel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETribal%20leader%20and%20Union%20minister%20Faggan%20Singh%20Kulaste%20contested%20from%20Niwas%20seat%20in%20Mandla.%20BJP%20general%20secretary%20Kailash%20Vijayvargiya%20was%20fielded%20in%20Indore-1%20against%20the%20popular%20Congress%20MLA%20Sanjay%20Shukla%20in%20one%20of%20the%20toughest%20battles%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20in%20the%20Datia%20constituency%20would%20also%20be%20well-watched%20as%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20candidate%20and%20senior%20minister%20Narottam%20Mishra%2C%20a%20CM%20post%20hopeful%2C%20had%20narrowly%20won%20last%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20and%20leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Govind%20Singh%20contested%20from%20Lahar%2C%20a%20seat%20he%20has%20held%20since%201990%2C%20in%20Raghogarh%20constituency%2C%20a%20seat%20never%20won%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20Jaivardhan%20Singh%2C%20the%20son%20of%20Congress%20veteran%20Digvijaya%20Singh%2C%20would%20look%20to%20repeat%20his%20success%20of%202013%20and%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20contest%20in%20Hoshangabad%20seat%20also%20intrigued%20observers%20as%20the%20Congress%20fielded%20a%20BJP%20rebel%20and%20former%20legislator%20Girija%20Shankar%20Sharma%20against%20his%20brother%20and%20sitting%20BJP%20MLA%20Sitasharan%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701518596000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13192647%2FF0g9YnHagAEuCqI.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcan-disenchantment-and-fatigue-trump-an-18-year-old-bjp-record-in-madhya-pradesh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Opposition%20Congress%20seized%20the%20initiative%20early-on%20as%20the%20saffron%20party%20trailed%20in%20the%20perception%20game%20for%20most%20of%20this%20year.%20The%20Congress%2C%20by%20causing%20defections%20of%20key%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20which%20coincided%20with%20a%20cloud%20of%20doubt%20hovering%20over%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20own%20future%2C%20appeared%20to%20be%20in%20the%20driving%20seat.%20But%20BJP%20has%20'made%20up'%20the%20gap%2C%20say%20others.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcan-disenchantment-and-fatigue-trump-an-18-year-old-bjp-record-in-madhya-pradesh%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tamil%20Nadu%3A%20ED%20Official%20Arrested%20in%20Bribery%20Case%20Sent%20to%2015-Day%20Police%20Custody%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29180215%2FThe-Wire-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20official%20arrested%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Police%20allegedly%20for%20accepting%20bribe%20has%20been%20sent%20to%2015-day%20police%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20December%201%2C%20the%20state%20police%20arrested%20ED%20official%20Ankit%20Tiwari%2C%20alleging%20that%20he%20had%20been%20caught%20%E2%80%9Cred-handed%E2%80%9D%20while%20accepting%20a%20bribe%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20from%20a%20doctor%20in%20the%20Dindigul%20district.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20hours%20after%20the%20arrest%2C%20the%20state%20police%20on%20Friday%20also%20raided%20the%20central%20probe%20agency%20office%20in%20Madurai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1730607708351652064%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Equoted%20by%20news%20agencies%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20saying%20that%20Tiwari%20along%20with%20his%20team%20of%20ED%20officers%20had%20been%20threatening%20several%20people%20and%20receiving%20bribes%20in%20the%20name%20of%20closing%20their%20case%20at%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate.%20DVAC%20(Directorate%20of%20Vigilance%20and%20Anti-Corruption)%20officials%20caught%20him%20with%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20cash%20in%20Dindigul.%20The%20investigation%20is%20underway.%20DVAC%20also%20searched%20the%20ED%20Office%20in%20Madurai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiwari%20and%20his%20team%20intimidated%20and%20received%20bribes%20from%20several%20persons%20in%C2%A0exchange%C2%A0of%20dropping%20charges%20against%20them%2C%20the%20police%20alleged%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftamil-nadu%2Falleged-ed-official-arrested-in-tamil-nadu-for-taking-bribes-to-close-cases%5C%22%3Eas%20per%20%3Cem%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%20This%20alleged%20bribery%20racket%20was%20discovered%20months%20after%20ED%20raids%20on%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%20leaders%20and%20their%20associates.%20Former%20minister%20for%20Electricity%2C%20Prohibition%2C%20and%20Excise%20V.%20Senthil%20Balaji%20was%20arrested%20earlier%20this%20year%20by%20ED%20for%20his%20cash-for-jobs%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%3Cem%3E%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%20that%20Tiwari%20is%20a%202016-batch%20officer%2C%20who%20had%20previously%20served%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Ftamil-nadu-police-arrest-senior-ed-officer-for-accepting-bribe-of-rs-20-lakh-9050047%2F%5C%22%3Eis%20currently%20posted%20in%20Madurai.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20Higher%20Education%20Minister%20K%20Ponmudi%E2%80%99s%20home%20in%20Villupuram%20was%20also%20raided%20by%20ED.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20this%20year%2C%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Anti-Corruption%20Bureau%20(ACB)%20arrested%20two%20ED%20officials%20on%20bribery%20charges%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20agency%20issued%20summons%20to%20the%20sons%20of%20the%20state%20Congress%20Committee%20Chief%20Govind%20Singh%20Dotasra.%20Dotasra%E2%80%99s%20sons%2C%20Abhilash%20and%20Avinash%2C%20had%20been%20summoned%20by%20the%20ED%20with%20reference%20to%20an%20alleged%20exam%20paper%20leak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20DMK-led%20state%20government%20had%20moved%20the%20Madras%20high%20court%20against%20ED%20summons%20to%2010%20district%20collectors%20as%20part%20of%20an%20investigation%20into%20alleged%20irregularities%20and%20malpractices%20in%20the%20mining%20and%20sale%20of%20river%20sand%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20The%20high%20court%20had%20stayed%20the%20summons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20the%20controversy%20regarding%20action%20by%20state%20police%20on%20central%20agency%20officers%20goes%2C%20there%20is%20a%20view%20that%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Vigilance%20and%20Anti-Corruption%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20is%20%E2%80%9Cwell%20within%20its%20jurisdiction%20to%20arrest%20an%20ED%20officer%20(Central%20Govt%20employee)%20on%20bribery%20allegations.%20With%20the%20State%20Govt%20revoking%20General%20Consent%20to%20CBI%20under%20Sec%206%20of%20DSPE%20Act%2C%20State%20Police%20has%20sole%20jurisdiction%20over%20Central%20Govt%20employees%20too%20in%20its%20territory%20under%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%20high%20court%20in%20a%20judgement%20this%20year%20ruled%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20special%20provision%20in%20the%20P.C%20Act%20or%20DSPE%20Act%20excluding%20or%20preventing%20the%20State%20police%20or%20a%20Special%20Agency%20of%20the%20State%20from%20investigating%20cases%20relating%20to%20the%20corruption%20of%20the%20Central%20Government%20employees.%20None%20of%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20P.C%20Act%20or%20DSPE%20Act%20authorises%20CBI%20or%20Central%20Vigilance%20Commission%20or%20any%20other%20Central%20Government%20Agency%20alone%20to%20investigate%20in%20matters%20relating%20to%20the%20Central%20Government%20employees%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EKerala%20HC%20in%20a%202023%20judgment%20has%20held%20as%20follows%3A%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20special%20provision%20in%20the%20P.C%20Act%20or%20DSPE%20Act%20excluding%20or%20preventing%20the%20State%20police%20or%20a%20Special%20Agency%20of%20the%20State%20from%20investigating%20cases%20relating%20to%20the%20corruption%20of%20the%20Central%20Government%20employees.%20None%20of%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FyoV41Nr7VC%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.c