able%20to%20persuade%20Washington%20not%20to%20make%20too%20much%20of%20the%20alleged%20Indian%20plot%20to%20kill%20a%20United%20States%20citizen%2C%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%20on%20American%20soil.%20After%20all%2C%20the%20Americans%20have%2C%20for%20multiple%20reasons%2C%20put%20all%20their%20eggs%20in%20the%20Modi%20basket.%20In%20fact%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20seems%20to%20be%20in%20the%20totally%20envious%20position%20of%20being%20the%20preferred%20choice%20of%20both%20Washington%20and%20Moscow%20for%20leadership%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20though%20for%20different%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20convergence%20of%20transactional%20calculations%20between%20Moscow%20and%20Washington%20may%20be%20found%20enormously%20satisfactory%20by%20the%20geopolitical%20elements%20of%20the%20ruling%20class%20in%20New%20Delhi%3B%20but%2C%20it%20would%20be%20comforting%20to%20believe%20that%20saner%20and%20sober%20citizens%20are%20finally%20coming%20to%20understand%20the%20enormous%20damage%20that%20the%20Modi%20persona%20has%20inflicted%20on%20the%20Indian%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20community%20may%20choose%20to%20take%20at%20face%20value%20our%20official%20assertion%20that%20assassinations%20and%20hit%20jobs%20are%20not%20%E2%80%9Cour%20policy%E2%80%9D%20but%20vast%20sections%20of%20Indian%20society%20have%20experienced%20for%20themselves%20the%20liberties%20our%20ruling%20coterie%20has%20taken%20with%20norms%20and%20laws%20%E2%80%93%20all%20the%20while%20maintaining%20the%20fa%C3%A7ade%20of%20observed%20legalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2FPannun%20capers%20can%20only%20be%20understood%20as%20wages%20of%20%E2%80%9C56-inch-ism.%E2%80%9D%20%C2%A0Nine%20years%20ago%2C%20our%20otherwise%20surefooted%20strategic%20establishment%20fell%20for%20the%20mythology%20that%20had%20been%20crafted%20by%20the%20Modi%20crowd%20for%20capturing%20political%20power%3A%20that%20a%20weak%20and%20timid%20political%20leadership%20%5Bexemplified%20by%20the%20polite%20and%20soft-spoken%20Dr.%20Manmohan%20Singh%5D%20had%20held%20India%20back%20from%20achieving%20its%20potential%20for%20greatness.%20After%20decades%2C%20India%20now%20had%20a%20prime%20minister%20who%20was%20flaunting%20his%20physical%20agility%20and%20swagger%20as%20a%20metaphor%20for%20national%20power%20and%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01141008%2FPannun-FP.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01141008%2FPannun-FP.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01141008%2FPannun-FP-300x150.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01141008%2FPannun-FP-1024x512.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01141008%2FPannun-FP-800x400.png%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687240%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40SFJGenCounsel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20middle%20classes%2C%20especially%20those%20with%20a%20son%20or%20a%20daughter%20in%20North%20America%2C%20were%20the%20most%20eager%20suckers%20for%20this%20bravado.%20The%20tall%20talk%20of%20%E2%80%9Csorting%E2%80%9D%20out%20Pakistan%20or%20looking%20China%20straight%20in%20the%20eye%20was%20catnip%20to%20the%20masses.%20Big%20business%2C%20too%2C%20went%20along%20because%20this%20bluster%20meant%20India%20having%20to%20purchase%20or%20build%20more%20and%20more%20weapon%20systems.%20War-mongering%20has%20always%20been%20good%20for%20businessmen.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20generals%20and%20admirals%20were%20grinning%20from%20ear%20to%20ear%20too%3B%20here%20at%20last%20was%20a%20prime%20minister%20who%20understood%20the%20business%20of%20conflicts%20and%20wars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20most%20cunning%20subscribers%20of%20this%20%E2%80%9C56-inch-ism%E2%80%9D%20were%20the%20overlords%20of%20the%20security%20establishment.%20These%20shadowy%20men%20quickly%20sized%20up%20our%20new%20saviour%2C%20decoded%20his%20insecurities%20and%20worked%20on%20his%20megalomania%3B%20they%20understood%20the%20great%20man%E2%80%99s%20need%20for%20%E2%80%9Cenemies%E2%80%9D%20to%20be%20tamed%20and%20vanquished.%20These%20%E2%80%9Csecurity-%20%3Cem%3Ewallahs%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20produced%20a%20whole%20roster%20of%20enemies%3A%20urban%20naxals%2C%20%E2%80%9Ctukde%20tukde%20gangs%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Kashmiris%2C%20the%20minorities%2C%20the%20farmers%2C%20the%20terrorists%2C%20the%20subversives%2C%20etc.%2C%20to%20be%20conquered%20and%20eliminated%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cthreat%E2%80%9D%20to%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20security%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cunity%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cintegrity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20higher%20the%20level%20of%20threat%20that%20these%20enemies%20were%20deemed%20to%20be%20capable%20of%20making%20against%20India%20and%20its%20greatest%20saviour%2C%20the%20greater%20were%20the%20powers%20granted%20to%20all%20those%20institutions%20and%20agencies%20which%20deal%20in%20the%20currency%20of%20violence%20and%20intimidation%20and%20coercion.%20An%20appropriately%20impressed%20judiciary%20went%20along%20with%20the%20security%20crowd%E2%80%99s%20definitions%20and%20interpretations%20of%20the%20needs%20of%20national%20security.%20The%20judiciary%2C%20at%20least%20at%20the%20lower%20levels%2C%20was%20even%20prepared%20to%20put%20anyone%20in%20jail%20who%20dared%20to%20mock%20or%20ridicule%20the%20prime%20minister.%C2%A0%20His%20%E2%80%9Cimage%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cprestige%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cdignity%E2%80%9D%20are%20now%20inextricably%20tied%20up%20with%20the%20defence%20and%20well-being%20of%20the%20realm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nijjar%2FPannun%20capers%20can%20be%20understood%20only%20in%20this%20demonology%2C%20crafted%20and%20scripted%20by%20cunning%20security%20managers.%20These%20crafty%20operatives%20felt%20enthused%20and%20empowered%20because%20their%20principal%20was%20equally%20adept%20at%20using%20the%20%E2%80%9Cenemies%E2%80%9D%20conjured%20up%20by%20them%20to%20tickle%20the%20average%20Hindu%E2%80%99s%20sense%20of%20insecurity.%20Having%20tamed%20the%20Muslims%20into%20submission%2C%20it%20was%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20before%20the%20Sikhs%20would%20get%20singled%20out%20as%20a%20source%20of%20new%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20those%20who%20live%20in%20Punjab%20will%20laugh%20at%20the%20suggestion%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CKhalistanis%E2%80%9D%20pose%20any%20kind%20of%20existential%20threat%20to%20India.%20There%20is%20no%20%E2%80%9CKhalistani%E2%80%9D%20constituency%20in%20Punjab.%20But%20the%20security%20managers%20know%20our%20political%20masters%E2%80%99%20need%20for%20%E2%80%9Cenemies%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthreats%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%2C%20by%20now%2C%20have%20become%20adept%20at%20weaving%20the%20Vishwaguru%20balderdash%20into%20their%20own%20empire-building%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Israel%20can%20go%20after%20its%20enemies%20beyond%20its%20borders%2C%20why%20can%E2%80%99t%20India%2C%20endowed%20as%20it%20is%20with%20decisive%20leadership%2C%20sort%20out%20those%20who%20dare%20to%20mock%20and%20challenge%20us%20from%20the%20safety%20of%20Canada%20or%20the%20United%20States%3F%20If%20American%20agents%20can%20take%20care%20of%20Iranian%20Commander%20Qassem%20Soleimani%2C%20we%20%C2%A0can%20at%20least%20finance%20a%20%3Cem%3Ejuggad%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20do%20in%20a%20Pannun.%20The%20political%20masters%20could%20not%20possibly%20object%2C%20as%20they%20knew%20how%20the%20Nijjar%20business%20was%20applauded%20in%20%E2%80%98nationalistic%E2%80%9D%20quarters%20as%20India%E2%80%99s%20coming%20of%20age%20as%20a%20truly%20global%20player.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20over-reach%20was%20an%20inevitable%20downstream%20effect%20of%20the%20phony%2056-inch-ism.%20We%20miscalculate%20and%20over-talk%20and%20over-sell%20our%20limited%20capacities%20and%20mediocre%20competence%20just%20because%20we%20can%20gather%20a%20howling%20crowd%20in%20Houston%20or%20New%20York%20we%20allow%20ourselves%20to%20dream%20global%20dreams%20%E2%80%93%20and%20feel%20unapologetically%20good%20about%20our%20new%20%E2%80%9Cstature.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Pannun%20business%20is%20a%20reminder%20of%20the%20damage%20that%20bogus%20political%20masters%20have%20inflicted%20on%20the%20well-being%20of%20all%20our%20national%20institutions.%20Unrelenting%20aggression%20against%20political%20rivals%20and%20foes%20has%20now%20corroded%20the%20judgment%20and%20wisdom%20of%20all%20those%20empowered%20savants%20whose%20duty%20it%20is%20to%20safeguard%20the%20core%20of%20our%20nation%E2%80%99s%20abiding%20interests%20from%20the%20excesses%20of%20the%20petty%20demagogue.%20No%20%3Cem%3Eacche%20din%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20the%20Indian%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fhkhare%5C%22%3EHarish%20Khare%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20former%20editor-in-chief%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3EThe%20Tribune%3Ci%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701517602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F26082650%2F33F81A3F-BCF6-4D05-975C-264958F029F4_1_105_c.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fpannun-nijjar-and-the-constant-need-to-find-the-enemies-of-modis-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20most%20cunning%20subscribers%20of%20Modi's%20%E2%80%9C56-inch-ism%E2%80%9D%20were%20the%20overlords%20of%20the%20security%20establishment.%20These%20shadowy%20men%20quickly%20sized%20up%20our%20new%20saviour%20and%20understood%20the%20great%20