india.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105679597.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIn%20response%20to%20a%20fan%20query%20about%20the%20post-movie%20sentiment%2C%20SRK%20shared%2C%20%E2%80%9CLove%20for%20family%20and%20your%20country%2C%20between%20giggles%20and%20laughter.%20%23Dunki%E2%80%9D%20The%20highly%20anticipated%20emotional%20drama%2C%20'Dunki%2C'%20directed%20by%20Rajkumar%20Hirani%20and%20starring%20SRK%2C%20is%20slated%20for%20release%20on%20December%2022.%20The%20recently%20unveiled%20Drop%202%20and%20Drop%203%20have%20captivated%20audiences%2C%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20the%20magical%20storytelling%20akin%20to%20the%20director's%20acclaimed%20work%20in%20'3%20Idiots'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2270-Year-Old%20Woman%20in%20Uganda%20Gives%20Birth%20to%20Twins%20After%20Fertility%20Treatment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2070-year-old%20Ugandan%20woman%2C%20Safina%20Namukwaya%2C%20defied%20expectations%20and%20became%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20oldest%20new%20mothers%20after%20successfully%20giving%20birth%20to%20twins%20through%20in%20vitro%20fertilization%20(IVF)%20treatment.%20The%20twins%2C%20a%20boy%20and%20a%20girl%2C%20were%20delivered%20via%20cesarean%20section%20on%20Wednesday%20at%20a%20hospital%20in%20Kampala%2C%20where%20Ms%20Namukwaya%20had%20received%20IVF%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67577038%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20hospital%20congratulated%20her%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20more%20than%20a%20%26quot%3Bmedical%20success%3B%20it's%20about%20the%20strength%20and%20resilience%20of%20the%20human%20spirit%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Edward%20Tamale%20Sali%2C%20a%20fertility%20specialist%20at%20the%20Women's%20Hospital%20International%20and%20Fertility%20Centre%20(WHI%26amp%3BFC)%2C%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20mother%20used%20a%20donor%20egg%20and%20her%20partner's%20sperm%20for%20the%20in-vitro%20fertilisation%20(IVF)%20procedure.%20The%20babies%20were%20born%20prematurely%20at%2031%20weeks%20and%20placed%20in%20incubators.%20Dr%20Sali%20says%20they%20are%20currently%20%26quot%3Bstable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20achieved%20the%20extraordinary-delivering%20twins%20to%20Africa's%20oldest%20mother%2C%20aged%2070!%26quot%3B%20the%20Women's%20Hospital%20International%20and%20Fertility%20Centre%20posted%20on%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffb.watch%2FoGOtw0uZ2E%2F%5C%22%3EFacebook%20page.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20historic%20event%2C%20a%20baby%20boy%20and%20girl%2C%20not%20only%20marks%20our%20two%20decades%20of%20leadership%20in%20IVF%20but%20also%20sets%20us%20apart%20as%20the%20premier%20fertility%20centre%20in%20Africa.Namukwaya%20delivered%20her%20babies%20today%20on%20Wednesday%2029th%20November%20at%2012%3A04%20pm%20Mother%20and%20babies%20are%20all%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20BBC%2C%20this%20is%20Ms%20Namukwaya's%20second%20delivery%20in%20three%20years.%20She%20gave%20birth%20to%20a%20baby%20girl%20in%202020.%20She%20said%20she%20had%20wanted%20to%20have%20children%20after%20she%20was%20mocked%20for%20being%20childless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMen%20don't%20like%20to%20be%20told%20that%20you%20are%20carrying%20more%20than%20one%20child.%20Ever%20since%20I%20was%20admitted%20here%2C%20my%20man%20has%20never%20showed%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Namukwaya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20looked%20after%20people's%20children%20and%20saw%20them%20grow%20up%20and%20leave%20me%20alone.%20I%20wondered%20who%20would%20take%20care%20of%20me%20when%20I%20grow%20old%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20is%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701515400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fa65pd5j