2%80%9CThe%20Cabinet%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20decided%20that%20the%20Central%20government%20will%20provide%20free%20food%20grains%20to%20about%2081.35%20crore%20beneficiaries%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Garib%20Kalyan%20Anna%20Yojana%20(PMGKAY)%20for%20a%20period%20of%20five%20years%20with%20effect%20from%201st%20January%2C%202024%E2%80%A6%20This%20is%20a%20historic%20decision%20that%20places%20PMGKAY%20amongst%20the%20World%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20social%20welfare%20schemes%20aimed%20at%20ensuring%20food%20and%20nutrition%20security%20for%2081.35%20crore%20persons%2C%20at%20an%20estimated%20cost%20of%20Rs.%2011.80%20lakh%20crore%20over%20a%205-year%20period%E2%80%A6%20The%20decision%20reflects%20the%20strong%20commitment%20of%20Hon.%20PM%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%20towards%20efficient%20and%20targeted%20welfare%20through%20fulfilment%20of%20basic%20food%20and%20nutrition%20requirements%20of%20the%20population.%20Ensuring%20food%20security%20at%20this%20scale%20during%20Amrit%20Kaal%20would%20play%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20dedicating%20efforts%20towards%20building%20an%20aspirational%20and%20developed%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20suo%20motto%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Felections%2Fchhattisgarh-assembly%2Fpm-modi-attacks-chhattisgarh-cm-cong-over-betting-app-row-says-they-didnt-even-spare-name-of-mahadev%2Farticle67497413.ece%5C%22%3Eproclaimed%20this%20largesse%20at%20an%20election%20rally%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20November%204%20this%20year.%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20poor%20brothers%20and%20sisters%20of%20the%20country%20from%20the%20land%20of%20Durg%20(Chhattisgarh)%20that%20I%20have%20decided%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20will%20now%20extend%20the%20PMGKAY%20providing%20free%20ration%20to%2080%20crore%20poor%20people%20of%20the%20country%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years.%E2%80%9D%20He%20claimed%20that%20he%20himself%20came%20from%20a%20poor%20family%20and%20he%20considers%20poor%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbiggest%20caste%20%5Bgroup%5D%20in%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20scheme%20involves%20free%20supply%20of%20five%20kg%20of%20food%20grains%20per%20month%20to%20over%20810%20million%20people%20who%20account%20for%20three-fourths%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20rural%20and%20half%20of%20the%20urban%20population.%20The%20scheme%20was%20initiated%20by%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government%20in%202013%20under%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act%20to%20provide%20subsidised%20food-grains%20to%20the%20poor.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20gone%20through%20changes%20since%20and%20the%20Modi%20government%20introduced%20the%20PMGKAY%20in%202020%20as%20a%20free%20ration%20entitlement%20scheme.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fmodi-amrit-kaal-hunger-unemployment%5C%22%3EHunger%20and%20Unemployment%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Amrit%20Kaal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fopinion%2Feditorial%2Fadmission-of-failure-to-reduce-poverty-hunger-2761143%5C%22%3Eextended%20for%20one%20year%20in%20December%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20country%20was%20recovering%20from%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%20and%20has%20been%20kept%20going%20with%20short%20extensions%20since.%20It%20is%20this%20scheme%20which%20is%20now%20being%20extended%20by%20five%20more%20years%20confirming%20the%20fact%20that%20majority%20of%20Indians%20are%20so%20poor%20that%20they%20cannot%20even%20afford%20to%20buy%20food%2C%20which%20is%20a%20basic%20necessity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20deep%20deprivation%20has%20accelerated%20during%20the%20NDA%20regime%20headed%20by%20Modi%20if%20one%20goes%20by%20the%20Gallup%20World%20Poll%20survey%20for%20India%20focusing%20on%20lack%20of%20money%20to%20buy%20food.%20The%20period%20covered%20in%20the%20study%20is%202018%20to%202021.%20About%2040.2%25%20of%20respondents%20in%20the%20survey%20reported%20not%20having%20enough%20money%20for%20food%20in%202018.%20This%20rose%20to%2048%25%20in%202021.%20In%202023%20it%20seemed%20to%20have%20climbed%20up%20further%20compelling%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sarkariallexams.in%2Fworld-news%2Fa-narrative-of-roti-kapada-aur-makaan-under-the-nda%2F-%5C%22%3Eextend%20the%20%E2%80%98free-ration%E2%80%99%20scheme%20to%20over%20half%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20five%20more%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20abject%20poverty%20is%20further%20evidenced%20by%20the%202023%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%20(GHI)%2C%20wherein%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globalhungerindex.org%2Findia.html%5C%22%3EIndia%20ranks%20111th%20out%20of%20the%20125%20countries%3C%2Fa%3E.%20With%20a%20score%20of%2028.7%20in%20the%202023%20GHI%2C%20India%20has%20a%20level%20of%20hunger%20that%20is%20serious.%20GHI%20is%20a%20peer-reviewed%20report%2C%20published%20on%20an%20annual%20basis%20by%20Concern%20Worldwide%20and%20Welthungerhilfe.%20The%20GHI%20is%20a%20tool%20designed%20to%20comprehensively%20measure%20and%20track%20hunger%20at%20global%2C%20regional%2C%20and%20national%20levels%2C%20reflecting%20multiple%20dimensions%20of%20hunger%20over%20time.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20aims%20to%20raise%20awareness%20and%20understanding%20of%20the%20struggle%20against%20hunger%2C%20provide%20a%20way%20to%20compare%20levels%20of%20hunger%20between%20countries%20and%20regions%2C%20and%20call%20attention%20to%20those%20areas%20of%20the%20world%20where%20hunger%20levels%20are%20highest%20and%20where%20the%20need%20for%20additional%20efforts%20to%20eliminate%20hunger%20is%20greatest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fformer-rbi-governor-raghuram-rajan-on-indias-economic-future%5C%22%3EFormer%20RBI%20Governor%20Raghuram%20Rajan%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20Economic%20Future%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20distressing%20is%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20low-income%20levels%20and%20deprivation%20is%20accompanied%20by%20it%20being%20among%20the%20most%20inequitable%20countries%20in%20the%20world%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Findias-richest-1-own-more-than-40-of-total-wealth-oxfam%2Farticle66381944.ece%5C%22%3Ethe%20richest%201%25%20owning%20more%20than%2040%25%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20total%20wealth%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20the%20bottom%20half%20of%20the%20population%20together%20share%20just%203%25.%C2%A0%20Reality%20is%20that%20the%20rich%20are%20getting%20richer%20while%20the%20poor%20are%20getting%20poorer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20in%20this%20canvas%20that%20a%20near%20ten-fold%20increase%20in%20the%20size%20of%20the%20economy%20and%20per-capita%20GDP%20is%20being%20projected%20to%20be%20achieved%20in%20the%20next%2025%20years.%20NITI%20Aayog%20recently%20announced%20the%20draft%20of%20the%20vision%20document%20%E2%80%98Viksit%20Bharat%20%40%202047%E2%80%99%20to%20make%20India%20a%20%2430%20trillion%20economy%20by%202047%20with%20a%20per%20capita%20GDP%20of%20%2417%2C590%20would%20be%20ready%20by%20December%2C%202023.%C2%A0%20America%E2%80%99s%20Boston%20Consulting%20Group%20would%20be%20readying%20this%20document%20in%20consultation%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Fvision-document-to-make-india-a-30-trillion-economy-by-2047-in-final-stages-draft-to-be-ready-by-december-9005032%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cbusiness%20tycoons%20and%20corporate%20honchos%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20including%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20and%20Gautam%20Adani.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENITI%20Aayog%20CEO%20BVR%20Subrahmanyam%20said%20that%20ten%20sectoral%20groups%20of%20secretaries%20from%20various%20ministries%20created%20around%20themes%20including%20infrastructure%2C%20welfare%2C%20commerce%20and%20industry%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20governance%20have%20each%20prepared%20a%20vision%20document%20in%20a%20process%20that%20lasted%20nearly%20two%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20claimed%20that%20the%20Indian%20economy%20is%20currently%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20fifth%20largest%2C%20with%20a%20size%20of%20%243.75%20trillion.%20The%20annual%20per-capita%20income%2C%20as%20per%20the%20government%20data%2C%20stood%20at%20%E2%82%B998%2C374%20in%202022-23%20i.e.%2C%20%241%2C183.%20Atanu%20Chakraborty%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20HDFC%20Bank%20expects%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Feconomy%2Findia-to-be-30-trillion-economy-by-2050-with-per-capita-income-of-21-000-hdfc-bank-chief-atanu-chakraborty-11697031442896.html%5C%22%3Ethe%20Indian%20economy%20to%20become%20the%20third%20largest%20in%20the%20next%20four%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20reach%20the%20%2430%20trillion-mark%20by%202050%2C%20with%20the%20per-capita%20income%20soaring%20to%20%2421%2C000%20by%20then.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBusiness%20tycoon%20Gautam%20Adani%20is%20more%20assertive%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adani.com%2Fblogs%2Findia-on-track-to-becoming-a-25-trillion30-trillion-economy-by-2050-says-gautam-adani%5C%22%3Echips%20in%20with%20this%20gem%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9CFollowing%20independence%2C%20it%20took%20us%2058%20years%20to%20get%20to%20our%20first%20trillion%20dollars%20of%20GDP%2C%2012%20years%20to%20get%20to%20the%20next%20trillion%20and%20just%205%20years%20for%20the%20third%20trillion.%20I%20anticipate%20that%20within%20the%20next%20decade%2C%20India%20will%20start%20adding%20a%20trillion%20dollars%20to%20its%20GDP%20every%2018%20months.%20This%20puts%20us%20on%20track%20to%20be%20a%20%2425-%2430%20trillion%20economy%20by%202050%20and%20drive%20India%E2%80%99s%20stock%20market%20capitalisation%20to%20over%20%2440%20trillion.%E2%80%9D%20And%20he%20adds%20to%20good%20measure%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20country%20is%20now%20the%20most%20exciting%20land%20of%20opportunities%E2%80%9D%20Indeed%2C%20he%20knows%20better!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20realise%20this%20dream%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Fvision-document-to-make-india-a-30-trillion-economy-by-2047-in-final-stages-draft-to-be-ready-by-december-9005032%2F%5C%22%3ENITI%20Aayog%E2%80%99s%20Subrahmanyam%20advocates%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Fvision-document-to-make-india-a-30-trillion-economy-by-2047-in-final-stages-draft-to-be-ready-by-december-9005032%2F%5C%22%3Edrastic%20changes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9C..2047%20will%20be%20a%20very%20different%20India.%20It%20will%20be%20highly%20urbanised.%20Where%20we%20live%2C%20the%20way%20we%20move%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20jobs%20we%20do%2C%20what%20we%20eat%E2%80%93things%20are%20going%20to%20change%20massively%20by%20that%20time%E2%80%A6%20The%20government%20needs%20radical%20restructuring%2C%20both%20horizontally%20and%20vertically%2C%20such%20that%20the%20lower%20levels%20of%20government%20be%20entirely%20tasked%20with%20implementation%20so%20that%20senior%20officials%20can%20spend%20more%20time%20ideating.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20pray%2C%20what%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdevelopment%20model%E2%80%9D%20to%20achieve%20this%20mammoth%20task%3F%20Predatory%20or%20participatory%3F%20In%20December%20of%202020%2C%20Subrahmanyam%E2%80%99s%20illustrious%20predecessor%20Amitabh%20Kant%20laid%20bare%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Freclaimtherepublic.in%2F2021%2F11%2F30%2Fprivatisation-an-affront-to-the-indian-constitution%2F%5C%22%3Eoligarchic-cum-monopolistic%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20promoting%20select%20champions%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20India%20a%20government%20has%20thought%20big%20in%20terms%20of%20size%20and%20scale%20and%20said%20we%20want%20to%20produce%20global%20champions.%20Nobody%20had%20the%20political%20will%20and%20the%20courage%20to%20say%20that%20we%20want%20to%20support%20five%20companies%20who%20want%20to%20be%20global%20champions.%E2%80%9D%20As%20the%20Adani%20story%20unfolds%2C%20we%20see%20this%20model%20being%20practiced%20with%20vengeance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20this%20model%20while%20hunger%20and%20extreme%20inequality%20persists%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20%2430%20trillion%20will%20go%20to%20one%20to%20two%20percent%20of%20the%20population%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20economy%20would%20look%20like%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20drunken%20stunted%20dog%E2%80%9D%20as%20described%20in%20Aseem%20Shrivastava%20and%20Ashish%20Kothari%E2%80%99s%20book%20%3Cem%3EChurning%20the%20Earth%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CImagine%20a%20puppy%20which%20is%20fed%20a%20special%20kind%20of%20diet%20which%20distorts%20his%20growth%20so%20that%20one%20of%20his%20legs%20grows%20astonishingly%20fast%2C%20while%20the%20other%20three%20get%20stunted%20to%20various%20degrees.%20Now%20imagine%20that%20the%20puppy%20grows%20into%20a%20dog%20of%20sorts%2C%20gets%20drunk%20and%20begin%20to%20spin%20around%20the%20house%20in%20ecstasy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20wonder%20whether%20this%20is%20the%20fate%20of%20%E2%80%98New%20India%E2%80%99%20in%20%E2%80%98Amrit%20Kaal%E2%80%99%20which%20the%20PIB%20note%20is%20talking%20about.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fm-g-devasahayam-2%5C%22%3EM.G.%20Devasahayam%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20former%20Army%20and%20IAS%20officer.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701514080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F13084433%2FIMG_1352.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Findias-amrit-kaal-hunger-inequity-and-a-30-trillion-economy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20near%20ten-fold%20increase%20in%20the%20size%20of%20the%20economy%20and%20per-capita%20GDP%20is%20being%20projected%20to%20be%20achieved%20in%20the%20next%2025%20years%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20poverty%2C%20hunger%20and%20unemployment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Findias-amrit-kaal-hunger-inequity-and-a-30-trillion-economy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Weeks%20After%20Indian%20Troops%20Asked%20to%20Leave%20Maldives%2C%20Modi%20Holds%20Talks%20with%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F02160923%2FEffect-9.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20COP%20summit%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20a%20series%20of%20discussions%20with%20world%20leaders%20ranging%20from%20his%20introductory%20meeting%20with%20the%20newly%20elected%20Maldivian%20president%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20to%20the%20first%20high-level%20interaction%20with%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20President%20Isaac%20Herzog%20after%20the%20October%207%20terror%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20interaction%2C%20Modi%20met%20with%20the%20Maldivian%20President%20in%20Dubai%20on%20Friday%2C%20two%20weeks%20after%20Muizzu%20won%20the%20presidential%20election.%20The%20meeting%20also%20took%20place%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Maldives%20government%20asking%20India%20to%20withdraw%20Indian%20defence%20personnel%20who%20were%20stationed%20to%20operate%20choppers%2C%20a%20day%20after%20Muizzu%20was%20sworn%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20island%20nation%E2%80%99s%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20outcome%20of%20the%20meeting%20was%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccore%20group%E2%80%9D%20as%20per%20India%20or%20a%20%E2%80%9Chigh%20level%20committee%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Maldives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20press%20note%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37325%2FPrime_Ministers_meeting_with_the_President_of_the_Republic_of_the_Maldives%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20two%20leaders%20%E2%80%9Cdiscussed%20ways%20to%20further%20deepen%20their%20partnership%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccore%20group%E2%80%9D%20was%20a%20result%20of%20this%20direction%20of%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldivian%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpresidency.gov.mv%2FPress%2FArticle%2F29241%5C%22%3Epress%20communique%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20declared%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Chigh%20level%20committee%E2%80%9D%20would%20be%20looking%20to%20enhance%20development%20and%20economic%20cooperation%2C%20people-to-people%20contacts%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fpresidencymv%2Fstatus%2F1730636900619481225%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Etweet%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Maldivian%20president%E2%80%99s%20office%20said%20that%20the%20two%20leaders%20%E2%80%9Cdiscussed%20cooperation%20between%20the%20Maldives%20and%20India%20on%20matters%20of%20concern%20and%20sensitivities%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Maldives%20and%20of%20mutual%20benefit%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20two%20countries%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2C%20however%2C%20no%20more%20details%20about%20the%20composition%20of%20the%20group%20or%20its%20discussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20key%20meeting%20was%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20talks%20with%20Israeli%20President%20Isaac%20Herzog.%20While%20Modi%20has%20spoken%20with%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20this%20was%20the%20highest-level%20meeting%20between%20India%20and%20Israel%20since%20Hamas%20launched%20a%20terror%20attack%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20an%20MEA%20readout%2C%20the%20two%20leaders%20exchanged%20views%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Congoing%20Israel%20%E2%80%93%20Hamas%20conflict%20in%20the%20region%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CPrime%20Minister%20expressed%20his%20condolences%20on%20the%20loss%20of%20lives%20in%20the%20October%207%20terror%20attacks%20and%20welcomed%20the%20release%20of%20hostages%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20reportedly%20emphasised%20the%20need%20for%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20need%20for%20continued%20and%20safe%20delivery%20of%20humanitarian%20aid%20for%20the%20affected%20population%E2%80%9D%20and%20recalled%20India%E2%80%99s%20support%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctwo-state%20solution%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20dispute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%201200%20were%20killed%20by%20Hamas%20on%20October%207%20and%20scores%20were%20taken%20hostage%20in%20Gaza.%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20counter-strikes%2C%20which%20included%20airstrikes%20and%20ground%20operations%2C%20killed%20over%2014%2C000%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seven-day%20pause%20in%20infighting%20to%20allow%20the%20return%20of%20hostages%20ended%20on%20Friday%2C%20with%20Israel%20resuming%20its%20bombardment%20of%20Gaza.%20India%20has%20not%20publicly%20urged%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20and%20it%20had%20abstained%20on%20the%20resolution%20in%20the%20UN%20general%20assembly%20which%20had%20called%20for%20a%20humanitarian%20pause%20to%20allow%20for%20supply%20of%20essential%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20PM%20also%20had%20meetings%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37326%2FPrime%2BMinisters%2Bmeeting%2Bwith%2Bthe%2BPresident%2Bof%2Bthe%2BFrench%2BRepublic%5C%22%3EFrench%20President%3C%2Fa%3E%20Emmanuel%20Macron%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37319%2FPrime%2BMinisters%2Bmeeting%2Bwith%2Bthe%2BPresident%2Bof%2Bthe%2BSwiss%2BConfederation%5C%22%3ESwiss%20President%3C%2Fa%3E%20Alain%20Berset%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37324%2FPrime%2BMinisters%2Bmeeting%2Bwith%2Bthe%2BPresident%2Bof%2Bthe%2BRepublic%2Bof%2BUzbekistan%5C%22%3EUzbek%20President%3C%2Fa%3E%20Shavkat%20Mirziyoyev%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37322%2FPrime%2BMinisters%2Bmeeting%2Bwith%2Bthe%2BPrime%2BMinister%2Bof%2Bthe%2BKingdom%2Bof%2BSweden%5C%22%3ESwedish%20PM%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ulf%20Kristersson%20as%20well%20his%20host%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37318%2FPrime%2BMinisters%2Bmeeting%2Bwith%2Bthe%2BPresident%2Bof%2Bthe%2BUnited%2BArab%2BEmirates%5C%22%3EUAE%20President%3C%2Fa%3E%20Sheikh%20Mohamed%20bin%20Zayed%20Al%20Nahyan.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701513804000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F02160923%2FEffect-9.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fweeks-after-indian-troops-asked-to-leave-maldives-modi-holds-talks-with-mohamed-muizzu%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20the%20sidelines%20of%20COP28%20in%20Dubai%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20held%20talks%20with%20the%20Maldivian%20new%20President%2C%20where%20both%20leaders%20'discussed%20ways%20to%20further%20deepen%20their%20partnership'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fweeks-after-indian-troops-asked-to-leave-maldives-modi-holds-talks-with-mohamed-muizzu%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20A%20Probe%20Agency%20Officer%20Extorted%20Rs%2040%20Lakh%20From%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Doctor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20officer%20arrested%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20was%20allegedly%20involved%20in%20an%20extortion%20racket%2C%20a%20complaint%20by%20the%20police%20has%20revealed.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20arrested%20an%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20officer.%20The%20FIR%20filed%20by%20Tamil%20Nadu%20police%20extensively%20details%20the%20role%20Ankit%20Tiwari%2C%20the%20arrested%20officer%2C%20played%20in%20the%20extortion%20racket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiwari%20used%20to%20text%20and%20message%20state%20government%20employees%20on%20WhatsApp%20using%20a%20fake%20name%20-%20Hardik.%20He%20would%20demand%20bribes%20on%20these%20calls%2C%20according%20to%20the%20complainant%20Dr%20Suresh%20Babu%20who%20ended%20up%20paying%20him%20Rs%2040%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20illegal%20transactions%20would%20often%20take%20on%20the%20highway%20during%20a%20journey%2C%20the%20complaint%20says.%20He%20met%20Dr%20Santosh%20when%20he%20was%20on%20his%20way%20to%20Madurai%2C%20and%20the%20negotiations%20took%20place%20during%20the%20journey.%20He%20received%20the%20first%20installment%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20bribe%20in%20cash%20in%20November%20and%20asked%20the%20money%20to%20be%20put%20in%20his%20boot%20which%20the%20government%20doctor%20says%20was%20recorded%20by%20his%20dash%20cam.%20The%20second%20installment%20was%20paid%20to%20him%20on%20a%20highway%20the%20same%20way%20and%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Vigilance%20and%20Anti-Corruption%20authorities%20who%20had%20laid%20a%20trap%20chased%20Tiwari's%20car%20to%20recover%20the%20alleged%20bribe%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Vigilance%20and%20Anti-Corruption%2C%20Mr%20Tiwari%20originally%20demanded%20Rs%203%20crore%20to%20%26quot%3Bavert%20legal%20action%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20case%20that%20had%20already%20been%20settled.%20He%20contacted%20the%20doctor%20on%20October%2029%2C%20claimed%20he%20was%20acting%20on%20instructions%20from%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20Office%2C%20and%20summoned%20him%20to%20the%20agency's%20Madurai%20office.%20When%20he%20came%2C%20Mr%20Tiwari%20accosted%20him%20and%20demanded%20the%20Rs%203%20crore%20bribe%2C%20which%20he%20later%20brought%20down%20to%20Rs%2051%20lakh%20claiming%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bspoken%20to%20his%20superiors%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20Ankit%20Tiwari%20nor%20his%20lawyers%20have%20made%20any%20remarks%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20police%20are%20already%20at%20loggerheads%20with%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20over%20the%20latter's%20summons%20to%20five%20district%20collectors%3B%20this%20is%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20probe%20into%20alleged%20money%20laundering%20linked%20to%20illegal%20sand%20mining.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cops%20are%20now%20investigating%20whether%20Ankit%20Tiwari%20had%20intimidated%20and%20received%20large%20sums%20of%20money%20from%20others%20and%20whether%20there%20was%20a%20nexus%20with%20other%20officials%20in%20Madurai%20and%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20close%20to%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20arrest%20of%20another%20ED%20officer%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20this%20has%20given%20ammunition%20to%20the%20opposition%20that%20alleges%20the%20Centre%20is%20deploying%20the%20probe%20agency%20to%20take%20on%20opposition-ruled%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701513600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Ft19estjg_tamil-nadu-ed-officer-arrested-_625x300_01_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftamil-nadu-news%2Fhow-a-probe-agency-officer-extorted-rs-40-lakh-from-tamil-nadu-doctor-4626940%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20officer%20arrested%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20was%20allegedly%20involved%20in%20an%20extortion%20racket%2C%20a%20complaint%20by%20the%20police%20has%20revealed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftamil-nadu-news%2Fhow-a-probe-agency-officer-extorted-rs-40-lakh-from-tamil-nadu-doctor-4626940%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftamil-nadu-news%2Fhow-a-probe-agency-officer-extorted-rs-40-lakh-from-tamil-nadu-doctor-4626940%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftamil-nadu-news%2Fhow-a-probe-agency-officer-extorted-rs-40-lakh-from-tamil-nadu-doctor-4626940%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Can%20A%20Woman%20Be%20Charged%20With%20Rape%3F%20Supreme%20Court%20To%20Examine%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECan%20a%20woman%20be%20booked%20in%20a%20rape%20case%3F%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20agreed%20to%20examine%20this%20question%20after%20a%20woman%20petitioned%20it%20for%20anticipatory%20bail%20in%20a%20rape%20case%20also%20involving%20her%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20asked%20the%20Punjab%20government%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20plea%20filed%20by%20a%2061-year-old%20woman%20who%20has%20been%20implicated%20in%20the%20case%20filed%20by%20her%20daughter-in-law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20agreeing%20to%20examine%20the%20issue%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Hrishikesh%20Roy%20and%20Sanjay%20Karol%20granted%20the%20woman%20protection%20from%20arrest%20and%20directed%20her%20to%20cooperate%20with%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIssue%20notice%2C%20returnable%20in%20four%20weeks.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20the%20petitioner%20is%20protected%20from%20arrest.%20But%20she%20is%20expected%20to%20cooperate%20with%20the%20investigation%20of%20the%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20outset%2C%20advocate%20Rishi%20Malhotra%2C%20who%20appeared%20for%20the%20woman%2C%20argued%20that%20all%20other%20penal%20sections%20in%20the%20FIR%20are%20bailable%20barring%20the%20charge%20under%20Section%20376(2)(n)%20IPC%20(repeated%20rape).%20Conviction%20under%20the%20section%20entails%20imprisonment%20of%20not%20less%20than%2010%20years%20and%20may%20extend%20to%20sentence%20for%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement%2C%20Mr%20Malhotra%20submitted%20a%20woman%20cannot%20be%20charged%20with%20rape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20case%2C%20the%20complainant%20was%20initially%20in%20a%20long-distance%20relationship%20with%20the%20US-based%20elder%20son%20of%20the%20woman%2C%20a%20widow%2C%20but%20they%20had%20never%20met%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20states%20that%20the%20complainant%20started%20living%20with%20the%20widow%20after%20entering%20into%20wedlock%20with%20her%20son%20at%20a%20virtual%20marriage%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20the%20younger%20son%20of%20the%20widow%20visited%20them%20from%20Portugal.%20The%20widow%20has%20claimed%20that%20after%20the%20arrival%20of%20her%20younger%20son%2C%20the%20complainant%20and%20her%20family%20pressured%20her%20to%20end%20the%20informal%20marriage%20with%20her%20elder%20son.%20When%20the%20younger%20son%20was%20about%20to%20leave%20for%20Portugal%2C%20the%20complainant%20insisted%20that%20he%20take%20her%20along%20but%20he%20left%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20tension%20mounted%20between%20the%20two%20families%2C%20a%20compromise%20was%20arrived%20at%20and%20the%20widow%20gave%20the%20complainant%20Rs%2011%20lakh%20for%20ending%20the%20marriage%20with%20her%20elder%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complainant%20then%20approached%20the%20local%20police%20and%20lodged%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20widow%20and%20her%20younger%20son%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20rape%20and%20other%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701513060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-07%2Fatt9hsso_court-generic_625x300_27_July_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcan-a-woman-be-charged-with-rape-supreme-court-to-examine-4626920%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Can%20a%20woman%20be%20booked%20in%20a%20rape%20case%3F%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20agreed%20to%2