a%20series%20of%20similar%20shootings%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20where%20three%20homeless%20people%20were%20killed.%20The%20police%20are%20investigating%20if%20there%20is%20any%20connection%20between%20the%20Las%20Vegas%20and%20Los%20Angeles%20shootings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ffive-homeless-people-shot-in-las-vegas-police%2Farticleshow%2F105677989.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ffive-homeless-people-shot-in-las-vegas-police%2Famp_articleshow%2F105677989.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ffive-homeless-people-shot-in-las-vegas-police%2Famp_articleshow%2F105677989.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BOnce%20Rohit%20Is%20Back...%26quot%3B%3A%20Ganguly's%20Straightforward%20Advice%20For%202024%20T20%20WC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EImpressed%20with%20his%20captaincy%20at%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20former%20captain%20Sourav%20Ganguly%20on%20Friday%20threw%20his%20weight%20behind%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20saying%20he%20should%20lead%20India%20at%20least%20till%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20June%20next%20year.%20Rohit%2C%20who%20led%20India%20to%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20final%20at%20home%2C%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20has%20taken%20a%20%26quot%3Bbreak%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20white-ball%20leg%20of%20the%20upcoming%20South%20Africa%20series%20beginning%20on%20December%2010.%20Talking%20to%20reporters%2C%20Ganguly%20said%20the%20duo%20deserved%20this%20rest%20so%20that%20they%20come%20back%20%26quot%3Bfresh%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20hectic%20calendar%20ahead.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20Rohit%20is%20back%20playing%20all%20formats%2C%20he%20should%20be%20the%20captain%20of%20India%2C%20because%20he%20has%20done%20so%20well%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20former%20BCCI%20president%2C%20who%20was%20named%20the%20Dabur%20Chyawanprash's%20brand%20ambassador%20for%20East%20India%2C%20during%20a%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20saw%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20how%20well%20they%20played.%20They%20are%20absolutely%20integral%20and%20an%20important%20part%20of%20Indian%20cricket.%26quot%3B%20Interestingly%2C%20both%20Rohit%20and%20Kohli%20haven't%20played%20a%20T20I%20since%20the%20semifinals%20against%20England%20in%20the%202022%20T20%20World%20Cup%20and%20the%20BCCI%20was%20not%20clear%20whether%20the%20duo%20should%20be%20in%20India's%20scheme%20of%20things%20for%20the%20T20%20global%20showpiece%20in%20six%20months'%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%202022%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20Hardik%20Pandya%20was%20named%20India's%20T20%20captain%20but%20following%20his%20injury%20during%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20is%20leading%20the%20team%20in%20the%20ongoing%20five-T20%20series%20against%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWorld%20Cups%20are%20different%20than%20a%20bilateral%20series%20because%20the%20pressures%20are%20different.%20They%20have%20been%20exceptional%20this%20World%20Cup%20and%20hopefully%20six-seven%20months%20down%20the%20line%20in%20the%20West%20Indies%20they%20will%20be%20again%20at%20their%20best%2C%26quot%3B%20Ganguly%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20(Rohit)%20a%20leader.%20I%20expect%20and%20I%20presume%20that%20he%20will%20continue%20as%20captain%20till%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%202024.%26quot%3B%20The%20duo%20will%20be%20back%20for%20the%20two-Test%20series%20in%20South%20Africa%20beginning%20with%20the%20Boxing%20Day%20Test%20in%20Centurion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVery%20rightfully%2C%20they%20have%20taken%20a%20break%20because%20there%20is%20so%20much%20cricket%20all%20the%20time.%20I%20cannot%20imagine%20that%20you%20played%20a%20World%20Cup%20final%20on%20the%2019th%20and%20in%20three%20days'%20time%20you're%20playing%20a%20T20I%20series%20against%20the%20same%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20Ganguly%20s