ar.%20ED%20is%20probing%20their%20alleged%20role%20in%20taking%20over%20control%20of%20the%20party%20mouthpiece%20%3Cem%3ENational%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20along%20with%20its%20half-dozen%20properties%20situated%20at%20prime%20locations%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Chandigarh%2C%20and%20Lucknow%2C%20and%20valued%20conservatively%20at%20hundreds%20of%20crores.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20went%20on%20to%20remind%20readers%20that%20this%20was%20the%20third%20time%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20had%20questioned%20the%20Gandhis%2C%20and%20that%20in%20August%202022%20also%20the%20ED%20had%20%E2%80%98searched%20the%20premises%20of%20Associated%20Journals%20Ltd%20at%20Herald%20House%2C%20on%20Bahadur%20Shah%20Zafar%20Marg%20in%20central%20Delhi%E2%80%9D%2C%20after%20grilling%20them%20for%20hours%20at%20the%20ED%20Headquarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnsurprisingly%20for%20the%20Modi%20era%20neither%20then%2C%20nor%20till%20today%2C%20has%20any%20newspaper%20considered%20it%20necessary%20to%20perform%20that%20most%20hallowed%20function%20of%20responsible%20journalism%2C%20which%20is%20to%20crosscheck%20allegations%20made%20against%20an%20indicted%20person%20or%20group%2C%20by%20getting%20their%20side%20of%20the%20story.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20not%20surprising%20that%20most%20newspaper%20readers%20now%20harbour%20the%20suspicion%20that%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20and%20its%20friends%20and%20associates%20in%20the%20Congress%20party%20are%20as%20corrupt%20as%20other%20run-of-mill%20politicians%20in%20our%20ramshackle%20democracy.%20This%20article%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20set%20the%20record%20straight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegation%20was%20first%20made%20by%20the%20political%20maverick%20Subramaniam%20Swamy%2C%20as%20a%20private%20complaint%20in%20the%20Rouse%20Avenue%20District%20Court%20in%C2%A0%20Delhi%20in%202012.%20Swamy%20alleged%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20headed%20by%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20had%20sold%20%3Cem%3EAssociated%20Journals%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20defunct%20company%20started%20by%20Pandit%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20in%201937%20to%20publish%20three%20pro-freedom%20publications%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ENational%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20English%2C%20%3Cem%3EQaumi%20Awaaz%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Urdu%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3ENavjivan%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Hindi%2C%20to%20a%20dummy%20company%20titled%20%3Cem%3EYoung%20Indian%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20for%20a%20song.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fexplainer-why-has-the-ed-summoned-the-gandhis-in-the-national-herald-case%5C%22%3EExplainer%20%7C%20Why%20Has%20the%20ED%20Summoned%20the%20Gandhis%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98National%20Herald%E2%80%99%20Case%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssociated%20Journals%20was%20defunct%2C%20but%20it%20owned%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20real%20estate%20in%20these%20three%20cities%20as%20well%20as%20in%20four%20others%20%E2%80%93%20Bhopal%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Indore%2C%20and%20Patna.%20In%202012%2C%20Swamy%20valued%20all%20of%20this%20at%20Rs%205%2C000%20crores%2C%C2%A0%20and%20alleged%20that%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20exercise%20was%20to%20give%20the%20board%20of%20%3Cem%3EYoung%20Indian%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethe%20right%20to%20sell%2C%20rent%20or%20develop%C2%A0%20AJL%E2%80%99s%20properties.%2076%25%20of%20the%20shares%20in%20%3Cem%3EYoung%20Indian%3C%2Fem%3E%20were%20held%20by%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20the%20remaining%2024%25%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FIndian_National_Congress%5C%22%3ECongress%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0party%20leaders%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FMotilal_Vora%5C%22%3EMotilal%20Vora%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FOscar_Fernandes%5C%22%3EOscar%20Fernandes%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%20Swamy%20argued%20that%20under%20both%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FRepresentation_of_the_People_Act_(India)%5C%22%3ERepresentation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%2C%201951%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%C2%A0%20Income%20Tax%20Act%20of%201961%2C%20it%20was%20illegal%20for%20a%20political%20party%20to%20lend%20money%20for%20commercial%20purposes.%20He%2C%20therefore%2C%20demanded%20an%20investigation%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20and%20de-recognition%20of%20the%20Congress%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20Swamy%20either%20deliberately%20or%20inadvertently%20overlooked%20was%20that%20there%20was%20also%20nothing%20untoward%20about%20creating%20a%20new%20company%20to%20buy%20and%20revive%20an%20old%20one.%20As%20president%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20had%20every%20right%20to%20revive%20the%20%3Cem%3ENational%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20for%20the%20paper%20had%20been%20founded%20by%20Pandit%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20in%201937%20with%20the%20express%20purpose%20of%20%E2%80%9Creflecting%20the%20policy%20and%20principles%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%E2%80%9D.%20It%20had%20got%20off%20to%20a%20flying%20start%20in%201937%20but%20never%20fully%20recovered%20from%20the%20blow%20it%20received%20when%20the%20British%20banned%20it%20in%201942%20for%20supporting%20the%20Quit%20India%20Movement.%20By%20the%20time%20the%20ban%20was%20lifted%20in%201945%2C%20the%20British%20were%20on%20their%20way%20out%20and%20Pandit%20Nehru%20and%20other%20senior%20leaders%2C%20who%20used%20to%20write%20for%20it%20regularly%20before%201942%2C%20were%20preoccupied%20with%20the%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F21155226%2FScreen-Shot-2018-12-21-at-3.50.11-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F21155226%2FScreen-Shot-2018-12-21-at-3.50.11-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F21155226%2FScreen-Shot-2018-12-21-at-3.50.11-PM-300x121.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F21155226%2FScreen-Shot-2018-12-21-at-3.50.11-PM-1024x413.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323407%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22484%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20offices%20of%20the%20National%20Herald%20newspaper.%20Photo%3A%20NH_India%2FTwitter%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20blow%20came%20in%20the%20mid-1980s%20when%20digital%20technology%20made%20it%20easy%20to%20produce%20a%20newspaper%20simultaneously%20from%20any%20number%20of%20centres.%20This%20killed%20smaller%2C%20regional%20newspapers%2C%20including%20the%20%3Cem%3ENational%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Lucknow%20and%20%3Cem%3ESearchlight%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Patna.%20Within%20a%20decade%2C%20scores%20of%20independent%20newspapers%20all%20over%20the%20country%20were%20closed%20down.%20By%20then%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ENational%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20become%20entirely%20dependent%20on%20annual%20handouts%20from%20the%20Congress%20party.%20In%202008%2C%20when%20these%20losses%20had%20mounted%20to%20Rs%2050%20crore%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20decided%20to%20call%20it%20a%20day%20and%20shut%20down%20the%20paper.%20Provident%20fund%2C%20voluntary%20retirement%2C%20and%20other%20minor%20closure%20raised%20the%20cumulative%20loss%20to%20Rs%2090.25%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20the%20Congress%20reversed%20its%20earlier%20decision%20and%20decided%20to%20revive%20the%20%3Cem%3ENational%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E.%20But%20Associated%20Journals%20was%20drowning%20in%20an%20ocean%20of%20debt%20and%20could%20not%20raise%20a%20paisa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20normal%20way%20of%20reviving%20any%20company%20in%20this%20condition%20was%20to%20convert%20all%20or%20a%20part%20of%20its%20debt%20into%20equity%20shares%20and%20sell%20these%20at%20a%20heavy%20discount%20to%20those%20willing%20to%20gamble%20on%20its%20recovery.%20This%20is%20a%20route%20that%20companies%20all%20over%20the%20world%20routinely%20take.%20Freed%20of%20the%20burden%20of%20interest%20payments%2C%20the%20company%20regains%20the%20capacity%20to%20borrow%20money%20and%20launch%20a%20new%20business%20plan.%20This%20was%20the%20route%20the%20Congress%20had%20decided%20to%20take.%20But%20to%20ensure%20that%20future%20profits%2C%20if%20any%2C%20went%20to%20the%20organisation%20and%20not%20the%20shareholders%2C%20it%20made%20%3Cem%3EYoung%20Indian%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20not-for-profit%20company%20under%20Section%2025%20(a)%20of%20the%20Companies%20Act.%20From%20then%20all%20the%20revenues%20that%20accrued%20from%20its%20properties%20went%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EYoung%20Indian%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Not%20a%20paisa%20came%20to%20the%20Congress%20party%20or%20its%20board%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20did%20not%20deter%20the%20Modi%20government%20from%20unleashing%20the%20ED%20upon%20the%20Congress.%20But%20when%2C%20after%20a%20full%20year%20of%20investigation%2C%20the%20ED%20concluded%20that%20there%20were%20no%20grounds%20for%20converting%20Swamy%E2%80%99s%20private%20case%20into%20a%20governmental%20inquiry%2C%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20fury%20broke%20all%20bounds.%20Rajan%20Katoch%2C%20the%20Director%20of%20the%20ED%C2%A0%20was%20dismissed%20overnight%2C%20along%20with%20Himanshu%20Kumar%2C%20his%20chief%20investigator.%20The%20new%20director%20was%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Mishra%20who%2C%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20did%20everything%20Modi%20wanted%20him%20to%20do.%20In%20flagrant%20violation%20of%20the%20long-standing%20rule%20that%20the%20ED%20chief%20had%20to%20have%20a%20fixed%20two-year%20tenure%20with%20a%20maximum%20extension%20of%20one%20year%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20gave%20Mishra%20extension%20after%20extension%20through%20Presidential%20ordinances%2C%20till%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20finally%20forced%20him%20out%20in%20September%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20five-year%20tenure%2C%20Mishra%20used%20the%20eight%20amendments%20to%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20pushed%20through%20parliament%20in%202019%20to%20turn%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20into%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20principal%20weapon%20for%20destroying%20the%20credibility%20of%20his%20political%20opponents%20in%20state%20after%20state.%20Among%20his%20principal%2C%20but%20by%20no%20means%20only%2C%20victims%20were%20Sanjay%20Raut%20and%20Anil%20Deshmukh%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Satyendra%20Jain%20and%20Manish%20Sisodia%20in%20Delhi.%20Other%20political%20party%20leaders%20who%20have%20been%20similarly%20hounded%20are%20P.Chidambaram%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20his%20son%20Karti%2C%20Hemant%20Soren%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20D.K.%20Shivakumar%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20throughout%20Mishra%E2%80%99s%20term%2C%20the%20principal%20target%20of%20the%20government%20has%20been%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20All%20the%20while%20that%20Mishra%20was%20overseeing%20the%20campaign%20to%20discredit%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20political%20opponents%2C%20Swamy%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98private%20complaint%E2%80%99%20had%20been%20dragging%20its%20way%20through%20the%20Rouse%20Avenue%20District%20Court%20with%20Swamy%20producing%20nothing%20to%20prove%20his%20allegations%20and%20failing%20to%20appear%20before%20it%20on%20date%20after%20date%20citing%20one%20excuse%20or%20another%2C%20until%20%3Cem%3Ehe%20himself%20asked%20for%20the%20prosecution%20to%20be%20stayed%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202022%2C%20therefore%2C%20Mishra%20resumed%20the%20attack%20by%20dragging%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20once%20more%20into%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20to%20answer%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20same%20allegations%20of%20money%20laundering%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20had%20been%20dismissed%20by%20Rajan%20Katoch%20in%202015.%20Over%20the%20next%20two%20months%20the%20ED%20interrogated%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20for%2050%20hours%20and%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20for%2010%20hours%2C%20but%20once%20again%20unearthed%20nothing%20new%20that%20could%20enable%20it%20to%20frame%20a%20%3Cem%3Eprima%20facie%3C%2Fem%3E%20case%20of%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20later%2C%20an%20alarmed%20Modi%20government%20facing%20an%20imminent%20general%20election%20against%20a%20united%20opposition%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20decided%20to%20go%20on%20the%20offensive%20once%20more.%20On%20November%2021%2C%20i.e.%20less%20than%20two%20weeks%20ago%2C%20it%20attached%20all%20the%20properties%20of%20Associated%20Journals%20and%20Young%20Indian%2C%20valuing%20these%20at%20Rs%20752%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20objective%20is%20not%20to%20prove%20anything%20%E2%80%93%20it%20has%20learned%20from%20all%20that%20has%20been%20described%20above%2C%20that%20there%20is%20not%20even%20a%20shred%20of%20evidence%20of%20wrongdoing%20by%20any%20member%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20%3Cem%3EYoung%20Indian%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20sole%20purpose%20of%20its%20charade%2C%20therefore%2C%20is%20to%20make%20a%20credulous%20and%20confused%20public%20believe%20that%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20who%20claim%20the%20mantle%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20freedom%20fathers%2C%20must%20have%20done%20something%20wrong%20to%20have%20caught%20the%20eye%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20a%20contemptuous%2C%20%3Cem%3Eunited%20%3C%2Fem%3Erejection%20of%20this%20thesis%20by%20the%20entire%20INDIA%20alliance%20will%20awaken%20doubts%20in%20the%20public%2C%20and%20foil%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20stratagem%20for%20winning%20the%20next%20election%20through%20false%20propaganda%20alone.%20That%20united%20voice%20is%20still%20to%20be%20heard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%2