Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Eclick%20here%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatever%20the%20final%20results%20of%20the%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20going%20by%20some%20credible%20exit%20polls%2C%20a%20noteworthy%20aspect%20is%20the%20caste-wise%20voting%20pattern%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20Rajasthan.%20This%20is%20particularly%20interesting%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20Opposition%20campaign%20to%20push%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20in%20various%20states%20and%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20radical%20shift%20towards%20wooing%20backward%20castes%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoll%20survey%20agency%20Axis%20My%20India%2C%20which%20has%20an%20excellent%20track%20record%20for%20accuracy%2C%20has%20done%20a%20detailed%20constituency-level%20survey%20for%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Egroup%2C%20which%20shows%20that%20in%20MP%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Chattisgarh%20there%20is%20fairly%20sharp%20caste%20polarisation%20wherein%20the%20BJP%20has%20a%20big%20lead%20over%20Congress%20in%20garnering%20OBC%20votes.%20However%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20ahead%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20capturing%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20votes%20in%20these%20three%20states.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20BJP%20also%20has%20a%20much%20higher%20share%20of%20upper-caste%20votes%2C%20which%20is%20a%20continuing%20trend.%20This%20polarised%20pattern%20needs%20to%20be%20examined%20by%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20for%20political%20strategising%20around%20the%20caste%20census.%20The%20key%20question%20is%2C%20to%20what%20extent%20will%20the%20politics%20around%20the%20caste%20census%20work%20in%20the%20cow%20belt%20states%20apart%20from%20Bihar%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%2056%25%20of%20OBC%20votes%20and%20the%20Congress%20has%20merely%2032%25%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Axis%2FIndia%20Today%20survey.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20Congress(45%25)%20leads%20the%20BJP%20(41%25)%20in%20securing%20SC%20votes.%20The%20Congress%20also%20has%20a%20lead%20of%203%20percentage%20points%20over%20BJP%20in%20the%20ST%20category%20in%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fneed-of-the-hour-a-selfie-called-caste-census-india-must-confront-its-truth%5C%22%3ENeed%20of%20the%20Hour%3A%20A%20Selfie%20Called%20Caste%20Census%20%E2%80%93%20India%20Must%20Confront%20its%20Truth%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Rajasthan%2C%20Congress%20with%2057%25%20SC%20votes%20massively%20leads%20the%20BJP%20with%20just%2026%25.%20Among%20STs%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Congress%20has%20a%2051%25%20vote%20share%20and%20BJP%20merely%2029%25.%20However%20among%20OBCs%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20equation%20reverses%20with%20the%20BJP%20having%2055%25%20and%20Congress%2029%25.%20That%20is%20a%20huge%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20distinctive%20and%20polarised%20pattern%20of%20voting%20among%20SC%2FST%20versus%20the%20OBC%20is%20interesting%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20politics%20around%20the%20caste%20census.%20Chhattisgarh%20shows%20a%20similar%20voting%20pattern%20for%20Congress%20and%20BJP.%20The%20BJP%20seems%20to%20have%20done%20well%20among%20OBCs%20in%20Chattisgarh%20by%20fielding%20a%20large%20number%20of%20OBC%20candidates%20from%20the%20Sahu%20community.%20This%20is%20also%20a%20bit%20surprising%2C%20given%20the%20overall%20popularity%20of%20Congress%E2%80%99%20much%20projected%20OBC%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhupesh%20Bhagel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Axis%20My%20India%E2%80%99s%20caste%20voting%20pattern%20is%20to%20be%20believed%2C%20then%20the%20Opposition%20alliance%20INDIA%20may%20have%20to%20think%20very%20hard%20about%20how%20to%20woo%20OBC%20voters%20in%20the%20Hindi%20belt%20outside%20of%20Bihar%2C%20the%20state%20which%20triggered%20the%20caste%20census%20politics.%20Bihar%20is%20the%20epicentre%20of%20the%20politics%20of%20OBC%20empowerment%20linked%20to%20the%20caste%20census%2C%20but%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20open%20articulation%20of%20a%20commensurate%20share%20of%20power%20for%20the%20OBCs%2C%20which%20began%20during%20his%20Karnataka%20election%20campaign%2C%20may%20face%20roadblocks%20where%20the%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20are%20in%20a%20direct%20fight%20in%20the%20Hindi%20belt.%20In%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20have%20to%20get%20a%20higher%20share%20of%20OBCs%20in%20MP%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chattisgarh%20to%20make%20a%20significant%20dent%20in%20the%20BJPs%20vote%20and%20seat%20share.%20With%20the%20OBCs%20and%20upper%20castes%20overwhelmingly%20voting%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20as%20indicated%20in%20the%20Axis%20My%20India%20survey%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20have%20to%20toil%C2%A0%20harder%20to%20work%20its%20new%20politics%20around%20the%20caste%20census%20in%20these%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20been%20able%20to%20make%20a%20big%20dent%20among%20the%20OBCs%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20perhaps%20in%20Telangana%2C%20where%20it%20was%20traditionally%20propelled%20by%20the%20upper%20caste%20Reddy%20community.%20However%2C%20the%20challenge%20of%20penetrating%20the%20substantial%20OBC%20vote%20bank%20in%20the%20broader%20Hindi%20belt%20remains%20quite%20daunting%20for%20the%20Congress.%20This%20task%20becomes%20tougher%20with%20the%20BJP%20managing%20to%20radicalise%20significant%20sections%20of%20OBCs%20towards%20Hindutva%20ideology%20in%20the%20cow%20belt%2C%20especially%20in%20UP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraditionally%2C%20when%20the%20Congress%20system%20flourished%20under%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20later%20briefly%20under%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20it%20enjoyed%20a%20substantial%20chunk%20of%20the%20SC%2C%20ST%2C%20Muslim%20and%20upper%20caste%20vote%2C%20which%20seemed%20an%20unbeatable%20combination.%20But%20today%2C%20the%20Congress%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20big%20chunk%20of%20the%20upper%20caste%20vote%20to%20add%20to%20the%20combination%20of%C2%A0%20SC%2C%20ST%20and%20Muslims.%20This%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20case%20in%20MP%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chattisgarh%2C%20where%20the%20Congress%20has%20a%20good%20chance%20of%20recovering%20from%20the%20collapse%20of%20its%20Lok%20Sabha%20tally%20in%202019.%20The%20BJP%20had%20almost%20swept%20these%20states%20in%202019.%20Penetrating%20the%20OBC%20vote%20in%20these%20states%20is%20therefore%20crucial%20to%20the%20exercise%20of%20the%20Congress%20reviving%20its%20fortunes%20in%20MP%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chattisgarh.%20This%20is%20especially%20so%20because%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20taken%20a%20decisive%20call%20to%20go%20for%20the%20OBC%20vote%20rather%20than%20focus%20on%20getting%20back%20the%20upper%20caste%20vote%2C%20which%20the%20Congress%20had%20lost%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701480641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29173721%2FEffect-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdespite-caste-survey-politics-is-obc-vote-eluding-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20a%20distinctive%20and%20polarised%20pattern%20of%20voting%20among%20SC%2FST%20and%20OBC%20communities.%20The%20key%20question%20is%2C%20to%20what%20extent%2C%20will%20the%20politics%20around%20caste%20census%20work%20in%20the%20cow%20belt%20states%20apart%20from%20Bihar%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdespite-caste-survey-politics-is-obc-vote-eluding-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bowen%3A%20US%20sets%20clearer%20red%20lines%20for%20Israel%20as%20ceasefire%20ends%22%2C%22content%22%3A%